cs glass lens create stunning images and protect your eyes. Perfect telescope for astronomers to explore stars and moon.\"},{\"text\":\"\\u3010High Magnification\\u3011Come with two replaceable 1.25\\\" eyepieces \\uff0c5x24 finderscope with mounting bracket and cross-hair lines inside make locating objects easily.\"},{\"text\":\"\\u3010Satisfaction\\u3011 2-year and lifetime maintenance. If you have any question about product and service, please feel free to contact us, we will do our best to help you\"},{\"text\":\"\\u3010EASY TO OPERATION\\u3011 No tools are required for refractor telescope even for the novice. Adjusted from about 17.7-inch to 35.4-inch. Allowed for many different observational positions and keep the whole tripod steady with castor wheel.\"}]\"', 69.99, 'gadget', 'img6_4N3O8W5I.png', 'https://www.ExcellentLifeDevice.com/img/img6.jpg', 0, NULL, 0),
(6, '3C7Q0F6J', 'Audio Systems, Multimedia Car Stereo', '\"[{\"text\":\"Answer\\/make calls and be hands-free with no distractions. The built-in microphone picks up your voice and your car speakers let you hear the person on the other side. Play and control your music and apps wirelessly\"}]\"', 69.99, 'gadget', 'img6_3C7Q0F6J.png', 'https://www.BestTechPiece.com/img/img11.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(5, '4Q3K6J7W', 'Automatic Soap Dispenser', '\"[{\"text\":\"Sleek and modern design, this auto soap dispenser will look beautiful in any kitchen or bathroom. It has the texture and appearance of Plastic. Easy to clean, just use a damp cloth and wipe it down.\"},{\"text\":\"Touch-free infra-red sensor - The smart motion technology gives you operation which is easy-to-use and does not need to have contact with your hand. The sensor will only be activated when needed, which can\'t be said for all soap dispensers. The soap is dispensed immediately thus enabling you to save time as well.\"},{\"text\":\"Avoid wasting your hand soap unnecessarily and avoid creating a mess that could emanate from applying too much pressure on a hand pumped hand soap dispenser. Small kids love using automatic hand soap dispensers; thus they will be looking forward to the next time they wash their hands thus cultivating a cleaning hands culture in them.\"},{\"text\":\"Work with hand sanitizer or liquid soap. Some soap dispensers require that you use a specific brand of soap, but this one gives you freedom. This can also be used in the kitchen as a dishwasher dispenser so that you can wash your dishes with ease. It adds beauty to your bathroom and kitchen which can\'t be seen with plastic hand wash bottles.\"},{\"text\":\"Are you sick of having to touch germy soap pumps and constantly replacing grimy soap bars that whittle away into a frustrating mess? It\'s time to bring the future to your bathroom and kitchen with an automatic soap dispenser. It has 400ml capacity you won\'t have to keep filling it up all the time.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 10 x 11 x 20.5 cm; Weight: 580 Grams.\"}]\"', 39.99, 'gadget', 'img5_4Q3K6J7W.png', 'https://www.AmazingHighTechWidget.com/img/img4.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(2, '4U1E7T1V', 'Automatic Whitening Massage Toothbrush', '\"[{\"text\":\"Different from traditional toothbrushes, we use a unique U-shaped brush head design, which fits the teeth better. The U-shaped design fits the mouth better, making it easier for babies to accept. Babies can brush their teeth while playing.\"},{\"text\":\"Made of food grade silicone. Safe material, no special smell, baby use more healthy. The silicone brush head is resistant to high temperature and can be disinfected at ordinary times.\"},{\"text\":\"U-shaped brush head design, 360\\u00b0 cleansing deciduous teeth. It is easier for babies to clean their teeth. Clean teeth in all directions to make the oral cavity healthier.\"},{\"text\":\"It\'s easy to use. the toothpaste and shake it in your mouth to clean teeth. Brush head can clean to all angles, so that brushing teeth becomes a simple thing. Shape similar to children\'s teeth: designed to thoroughly clean children\'s teeth. Kids always love to eat sweets, you don\'t have to worry about tooth decay and tooth decay.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 3.94 x 2.36 x 2.17 inches. Weight: 1.59 Ounces.\"}]\"', 6.25, 'gadget', 'img2_4U1E7T1V.png', 'https://www.EnjoyLifeDevice.com/img/img15.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(6, '7Q4L7C5K', 'BBQ Grill Utensil Tools Set', '\"[{\"title\":\"THE MOST COMPLETE KIT\",\"text\":\"This BBQ utensils includes 1 tong, 1 fork, 1 knife, 1 grill brush, 1 basting brush, 4 skewers, 8 corn holders, 1 replaceable head of grill brush, and 1 spatula that has 4 functions(with built-in bottle opener and tenderizer blades). This is a complete and professional grill accessories that contains almost everything you need for grilling.\"},{\"title\":\"PREMIUM MATERIAL\",\"text\":\"Grillart barbecue utensils is made from professional grade stainless steel that resists heat and stands the test of time. Unlike utensils made from wood or lower quality metals, ours do not crack, rust, or burn\"},{\"title\":\"SPECIAL DESIGN\",\"text\":\"User-friendly is our main design purpose. Reinforced BBQ tongs can easily clip food and is not easy to bend. The spatula is a 4-in-1 multi tool, which includes slotted turner with tenderizer blades and built-in bottle opener. Elongated stainless steel handles keep your hands at a safe distance from the flam while you grill. Hanging rings at the top of each handle enable easy storage during the off-season .\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 17 x 12 x 4 inches; Weight: 6.14 pounds; Color: Gray; Material: Stainless Steel\"}]\"', 69.99, 'gadget', 'img6_7Q4L7C5K.png', 'https://www.ExtraFunWidget.com/img/img6.jpg', 0, NULL, 0),
