(2, '3A6A5L6K', 'Cleaning Pen 4 in 1 Multi-Function', '\"[{\"text\":\" EARBUD CLEANING PEN CONSISTS OF FOUR PARTS: A Pen Tip, A Long-Haired Brush, And 2 Cleaning Brushes. earphone cleaning kit with Flocking Sponge, High-density Brush and Metal Pen Tip, dual head hidden design to meet a variety of cleaning needs\"},{\"text\":\"MULTIFUNCTIONAL FINE BRISTLE BRUSH\\uff1a Easily clean the dirt on the sound outlet hole of the earphone and other parts\"},{\"text\":\"METAL PEN TIP:Headset Cleaning Pen Uses The Tip to Keep The Pen in A Good Grip, Which Can Easily Clean Up Stubborn Residues And Keep Your Headset, Keyboard, Mouse Clean And Tidy.\"},{\"text\":\"FLOCKING SPONGE: Delicate and soft flocking sponge can clean the dust in the charging case of the earphone\"},{\"text\":\"WIDE APPLICATION: Besides earbuds, this cleaning pen can also be used to clean headset, mobile phone, computer, pad, camera and other digital products. \"}]\"', 6.95, 'gadget', 'img2_3A6A5L6K.png', 'https://www.BestWidgetStock.com/img/img21.png', 0, NULL, 0),
