(2, '3H1Y3D8T', 'Coffee Tamper', '\"[{\"text\":\"FANTASTIC QUALITY: Made of tumble finished long lasting cast alloy with no chemical coating that resists corrosion from acids found in coffee.\"},{\"text\":\"GREAT FUNCTION: The dual ends of this tamper evenly distributes, compress and level ground coffee for a denser, richer and more flavorful espresso brew; Features two flat tamping sides; 51mm (2-inches) and 58mm (2-1\\/4-inches).\"},{\"text\":\"GREAT FOR ANY KITCHEN: Commercial quality, heavy die cast aluminum alloy designed by a professional barista for the expert or home espresso maker.\"},{\"text\":\"VERSATILE: A must have for all baristas both professional and novice; Is also great to use in your kitchen to tamp and press pastry into pans or create mini slider patties.\"},{\"text\":\"EASY TO CLEAN: Simply hand wash with warm soapy water, dry thoroughly.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 2.75 x 2.25 x 2.75 inches. Weight: 4 ounces.\"}]\"', 6.95, 'gadget', 'img2_3H1Y3D8T.png', 'https://www.PopularToolZone.com/img/img19.png', 0, NULL, 0);
