(2, '0A3Q5L3K', 'Colorful Gradient Aquarium Light', '\"[{\"text\":\"Amphibious: Waterproof diving lights need to be used for diving completely, but they can actually be used both on land and on water. If water is not used, it will affect about 20% of its service life if it is not used in water.\"},{\"text\":\"Quality Materials: Fish tank spotlights are made of high-quality plastic materials, non-toxic, tasteless, environmentally safe, and have no effect on water quality and fish. Rugged and durable, with long service life.\"},{\"text\":\"Practical And Convenient: The colorful gradient aquarium light is equipped with a suction cup, which is easy to install and use. The angle of the light can be adjusted, and it can be adjusted to the desired position. Make your fish tank landscape more natural and vivid.\"},{\"text\":\"Multiple Benefits: The LED fish tank spotlight has a power of only 1W, and can be installed in the aquarium for lighting and decorative purposes. Just adjust the light to different angles and shine the fish in the water to create a beautiful scenery.\"},{\"text\":\"High Performance: The colorful aquarium lamp has fine workmanship, low voltage design, and safety voltage transformer. Can be used for fresh water\\/sea water tanks.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 0.39 x 0.39 x 0.39 inches. Weight: 3.17 ounces.\"}]\"', 6.95, 'gadget', 'img2_0A3Q5L3K.png', 'https://www.ThePowerfulWidget.com/img/img16.png', 0, NULL, 0),
