(9, '1X7G6P6C', 'Digital Wireless Backup Camera', '\"[{\"text\":\"No More Complex Wiring Problem. 7\\\" TFT rear view monitor connects a backup camera by a wireless transmitter.You just need to connect the monitor to the lighter charger, connect the camera to running light or reversing light and you are good to go. No more complicated long video cables from the monitor to the camera. Make all things much easier.\"},{\"text\":\"With digital wireless transmission, delivers a stable image without any interference from other signals such as Bluetooth. Equipped with great sensor, the camera provides vivid picture , which restores what you see behind your car directly.\"},{\"text\":\"The waterproof standard of this camera is IP69 , the highest and lowest temperature resistance is -4\\u00b0F~149\\u00b0F, and the lumen rating is 0.1 at low light night. Therefore whether it is sunny or rainy, hot or cold, day or night, the camera always performs well.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 11.5 x 6.97 x 2.36 inches; Weight: 1.7 pounds; Material: ABS Plastic; Color: Black\"}]\"', 139, 'gadget', 'img9_1X7G6P6C.png', 'https://www.HandyGadgetPro.com/img/img11.png', 0, NULL, 0),
