(7, '2M7X6I6N', 'Electric Shaver', '\"[{\"text\":\"Designed with your skin in mind, shaver lets you shave any way you want for a comfortable dry shave or refreshing wet shave with or without shaving cream or gel.\"},{\"text\":\"Protect your skin with our unique  shaving system to deliver a smooth shave that\'s gentle on your skin; Shaver effectively shaves both longer and shorter hair stubble.\"},{\"text\":\"The pivot, flex & float heads follow every contour of your face to remain in close contact with skin for a fast shave that\'s also gentle on your skin.\"},{\"text\":\"Ease of trimming with trimmer to help complete your facial hair grooming routine; Ideal for trimming sideburns, goatees, mustaches and more.\"},{\"text\":\"The rechargeable Lithium ion battery delivers the power of a corded shaver without the hassle of a cord with 50 minutes of shaving time.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 2.2 x 2.2 x 5.75 inches. Weight: 9.6 Ounces.\"}]\"', 89.95, 'gadget', 'img7_2M7X6I6N.png', 'https://www.GadgetTechMart.com/img/img7.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(9, '8Q5D0U5A', 'Electric Skateboard', '\"[{\"text\":\"Long Range&High Speed: Powered by 350W Motor, electric longboard with remote provides lithium-Ion-powered Electric skateboarding action at speeds up to 12 mph for up to 10 miles per charge. This electric skateboard for adults&youth is equipped with a secured 29.4V 2200mah Samsung lithium battery pack that can be fully charged within 2 hours. And you can ride it as a regular board without electricity.\"},{\"text\":\"Ergonomic Wireless Remote: 2 modes: Beginner and Advanced. 2.4G wireless remote controller with 4 Led indicators, the electric longboard with remote keep you informed of the skateboard battery level and controls speed. With the remote, you can control the skateboard to go forward, backward, accelerate and brake easily.\"},{\"text\":\"Solid Construction: The deck of the electric skateboard for adults&youth is made of 7 layers of rock-hard maple wood, which makes it flexible and durable for daily use and will support a rider up to 176 pounds. The electric skateboard for adults&youth is made of high-quality thick aluminum trucks and steel axles, making it reliable and sturdy, safe for beginners.\"},{\"text\":\"Smooth & Speedy Ride: High-grip PU wheels of the boosted board can greatly improve the shock absorption function and provide an unbelievably smooth riding experience. Kick tail designed for added control. Even in high-speed, this boosted board for beginners and professionals could keep sufficient stability and balance to ensure safety and a good riding experience.\"},{\"text\":\"Portable & Lightweight: The electric longboard with remote is light enough, only 12 pounds, with a handle, it\'s easy to carry. Package Content: 1 X Electric Skateboard, 1 X Power Adapter, 1 X Remote Controller, 1 X USB Charging Cable, 1 X Wrench, 1 X User Manual.\"},{\"text\":\"Deck Width: 8.6 Inches. Deck Length: 70 Centimeters. Dimensions: 5.3inch x 25.6inch x 4.7inch.\"}]\"', 132, 'gadget', 'img9_8Q5D0U5A.png', 'https:/