(10, '3R4X4Q6Y', 'Electric Snow Shovel', '\"[{\"text\":\"Versatile: Ideal for quick + easy snow pickups on decks, steps, patios and sidewalks.\"},{\"text\":\"Powerful: 8. 5-amp motor clears up to 9 tons of snow per hour.\"},{\"text\":\"Maintenance-Free: no pull cords, gas, oil, tune-ups or carbon emissions.\"},{\"text\":\"Durable: 2-blade high-impact, low-temperature paddle auger throws snow up to 20 feet and cuts a 10 in. x 6 in. path.\"},{\"text\":\"Package Dimensions: 52 x 12.6 x 10.6 inches. Weight: 12.1 pounds.\"}]\"', 141, 'gadget', 'img10_3R4X4Q6Y.png', 'https://www.ProGadgetWork.com/img/img14.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(8, '0G5Z4A5O', 'Electric Snow Thrower', '\"[{\"text\":\"Versatile: Ideal for quick snow pickups on small to mid-sized driveways and walkways\"},{\"text\":\"Maintenance-Free: No gas, oil or tune-ups make it effortless to start and maintain.\"},{\"text\":\"Powerful: 13-amp motor moves up to 550 lbs of snow per minute.\"},{\"text\":\"2-Blade Auger: Cold and abrasion-resistant plastic auger cuts 18 in. wide by 8 in. deep with each pass.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 54.5 x 19 x 26 inches. Weight: 34 pounds.\"}]\"', 119, 'gadget', 'img8_0G5Z4A5O.png', 'https://www.AmazingHighTechWidget.com/img/img9.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(8, '5A2U2K2P', 'Electric Spin Mop', '\"[{\"text\":\"Powerful Spin & Long-Last Battery - The powerful floor cleaner equipped with the dual-motor spinning up to 220r\\/min, removes stubborn stains, dust and splotch on the home and kitchen floor quickly. Meanwhile, it will automatically push the head of electric mop forward, making housework no effort. Compared to other electric mops, detachable 2550mAh battery of VMAI cordless mop provides a longer running time of 40-60 mins after only 2.5-3hrs fast charging, easily clean up to 2150 sq.ftarea.\"},{\"text\":\"Hands-Free & Lightweight - Our electric mop applied with the latest wireless technology, is unrestricted by distance. Together with less than 3 pounds self-weight and the ergonomic handle, let you mop around the house or take the cordless mop up and down stairs easily for floor cleaning. Stand-Free of the mop is convenient for storing. No-Touch disposal, no need to touch the dirty pad again. Floor cleaner for living room, kitchen, bedroom, bathroom.\"},{\"text\":\"Flexible, Adjustable and LED Headlight - The electric floor mop with an extendable rod for free length adjusting, is long up to 48.8 inches and short up to 37 inches, meeting different needs. No bending, no backache. The mop head allows 180\\u00b0 rotated from left to right, 90\\u00b0rotated for standing and facilitating mopping. It\\u2019s easier to reach beneath and around furniture. Flexible mop with LED headlight can remove the grime from those hard to reach place! Stain can\'t hide anymore!\"},{\"text\":\"Sprayer for Cleaning & Waxing - This electric mop provides spray function due to the 300ml built-in water tank. Fulfill clean water to the water tank by including measuring cup, you can mop while spraying. Or add wax oil to it, if you want to scrub the wooden floor. Just simply press and hold the spray button on the handle of the spray mop, you can control how much liquid you want. Perfect scrubber and cleaner for vinyl, tile, hard floor, wood floor, laminate floor, Marble Floor, etc.\"},{\"text\":\"Package Dimensions: 20.9 x 16.9 x 5.9 inches. Weight: 5.6 Pounds.\"}]\"', 109, 'gadget', 'img8_5A2U2K2P.png', 'https://www.AllBestTechTool.com/img/img8.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(6, '8Y5F6C0C', 'Electric Spin Scrubber', '\"[{\"text\":\"Newest Cordless Design: Handheld electric cleaner is cordless so it can be used anywhere, anywhere to get rid of the troubles caused by traditional power cord winding; The cordless scrubber is very lightweight, easy to pick up and use, can quickly clean the surface without fatigue, and improves the inconvenience of the conventional scrubber.\"},{\"text\":\"Make Cleaning Easier: The advantage of power scrubber rechargeable is that you can save your strength and reduce your burden when cleaning; The ergonomically designed handle is efficient, saves time and effort and reduces damage to the wrist and shoulders of the opponent; Take care of your hands and your home.\"},{\"text\":\"Efficient Cleaning, Powerful Battery: Floor scrubber, which can be rotated 360 degrees, quickly scrubs and cleans in the bathroom or kitchen at 350 RPM for improved cleaning efficiency; Built-in rechargeable 2200MHA battery, Power scrubber brush can work continuously for up to 60 minutes after 4-5 hours of fast charging; This is a good helper for cleaning.\"},{\"text\":\"Multi-brush Head, No Corner: The electric spin scrubber includes 3 brush heads to meet your different cleaning needs; The rounded brush is perfect for bathtub or sink; The flat brush is suitable for floor, tile, oven and stove; The pointed corner brush is great for cleaning window sill, corners and tight places, even bicycle wheels; Targeted use saves your energy; When pulling out the brush, it will be a little tight and need some strength; It is to prevent it from falling cause too loose.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 14.96 x 7.68 x 3.54 inches. Weight: 2.4 pounds.\"}]\"', 69.99, 'gadget', 'img6_8Y5F6C0C.png', 'https://www.AmazingHighTechWidget.com/img/img6.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(9, '4Q0F0J7W', 'Electric Stand Mixer', '\"[{\"text\":\"This mixer performs better than 2-beater stand mixers, and features the popular tilt-up head design for adding ingredients and changing attachments quickly.\"},{\"text\":\"Baking with ease: Effortlessly mix thick batters and doughs like breads, pizza, cookies, mashed potatoes and more with a powerful, 300 watt motor.\"},{\"text\":\"Complete bowl coverage: No scraping necessary. Mix hands-free with excellent results every time. Planetary mixing rotates the beaters around the 4 quart, stainless steel bowl, for even and complete mixing.\"},{\"text\":\"Mixing versatility: Includes splash guard, dough hook, whisk and flat beater. Wipe outside of stand mixer with a damp cloth or sponge and dry.\"},{\"text\":\"7 speeds and mixing guide: Go from a slow stir to a fast mix, with exact control at each setting. A helpful guide at the mixer\\u2019s top lets you know which speed to use for various mixing methods.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 10.4 x 15.55 x 16.3 inches. Weight: 12.48 pounds.\"}]\"', 132, 'gadget', 'img9_4Q0F0J7W.png', 'https://www.TrustOverWidget.com/img/img10.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(3, '8K8E4Z3L', 'Electric Stapler', '\"[{\"text\":\"JAM-FREE CARTRIDGE ELECTRIC STAPLER \\u2013 Productivity is priority with the speed and stamina of this tough, AC-powered electric stapler. Superior machine engineering for years of jam-free, heavy use.\"},{\"text\":\"CARTRIDGE INCLUDED \\u2013 Stapler comes pre-packed with a 5,000 staple cartridge, so you\\u2019re ready to start stapling.\"},{\"text\":\"SECURES 70 SHEETS \\u2013 Flat clinch stapling mechanism fastens up to 70 sheets of 20-pound paper for easy, neat stacking.\"},{\"text\":\"ACCURATE STAPLE PLACEMENT \\u2013 Precision alignment guide assists with accurate staple placement.\"},{\"text\":\"PATENTED CARTRIDGE - Patented cartridge technology delivers 5,000 staples without the need to reload. Stapler is designed for enhanced productivity, efficiency, and consistency.\"},{\"text\":\"SIMPLE DESIGN \\u2013 Sturdy and simple, this black stapler fits in neatly with other desktop supplies. Suction cups on the stapler\'s base keep the stapler securely in place during use.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 14.83 x 10.46 x 6.41 inches. Weight: 0.96 ounces.\"}]\"', 19.99, 'gadget', 'img3_8K8E4Z3L.png', 'https://www.skywardtechgadgets.com/img/img2.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(10, '1H8Y2L6N', 'Electric Tankless Water Heater', '\"[{\"text\":\"Can provide hot water for one sink at 0.5 GPM in warmer climates.\"},{\"text\":\"Requires 1 x 30 amp breaker and 10 AWG wire.\"},{\"text\":\"For one sink at 0.5 GPM in colder climates the POU 6 is recommended.\"},{\"text\":\"This product is recommended for use with a single sink only. Do not use with a shower or multiple fixtures.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 11 x 3 x 6 inches. Weight: 1 pounds.\"}]\"', 141, 'gadget', 'img10_1H8Y2L6N.png', 'https://www.OneBestGadgetStore.com/img/img12.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(4, '3D5J2F5L', 'Electric Tea Kettle', '\"[{\"text\":\"Fast & easy hot water: bring up to 1. 8 liters of water to a rapid boil, quicker than a microwave could do the job.\"},{\"text\":\"Automatic shutoff: have peace of mind knowing the kettle features boil-dry protection and will turn itself off after water boils.\"},{\"text\":\"Cord-free serving: the kettle lifts off the base so you can serve at the Table.\"},{\"text\":\"Dual water windows: lets you quickly see how much water is in the kettle when filling it.\"},{\"text\":\"Easy to pour: a drip-free spout eliminates mess, and the handle features a slip-resistant grip.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 9.75 x 6.12 x 10.53 inches. Weight: 2.2 pounds.\"}]\"', 24.99, 'gadget', 'img4_3D5J2F5L.png', 'https://www.OneBestGadgetStore.com/img/img3.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(4, '1G0U7A0B', 'Electric Toilet Brush', '\"[{\"text\":\"Smart USB charging and 360\\u00b0 rotating brush head: Smart button, one-key start, USB charging use, bid farewell to the traditional time-consuming and laborious toilet brush, the rotating speed reaches 200 RPM, deep cleaning requires no effort and works easily.\"},{\"text\":\"Good quality TPR toilet brush: Electric toilet brush head is made of wear-resistant TPR material, will not wear or deform, will not tangle the hair, will not stick to the dirt, will be cleaned after a flush, and will not damage the glaze. Designed for hard to reach places.\"},{\"text\":\"2200mAh large battery: Built-in 2000mAh lithium ion battery, which can last up to 3 hours when fully charged. Under normal conditions, it can be used for more than 120 days after cleaning once a day.\"},{\"text\":\"Removable toilet brush: Unique and innovative design, the toilet brush has ventilation holes, there is no water in the ventilation holes, it dries quickly, maintains hygiene, does not emit peculiar smell, and is equipped with a stable and water-free base, which is more comfortable.\"},{\"text\":\"Waterproof IPX7 : The toilet brush with reliable IPX7 waterproof design ensures safe use in wet conditions, without worrying about water damage to the machine, and its service life is greatly extended.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 16 x 2.9 x 16 inches. Weight: 1.61 pounds.\"}]\"', 24.99, 'gadget', 'img4_1G0U7A0B.png', 'https://www.AmazingHighTechWidget.com/img/img3.png', 0, NULL, 0),
