(5, '5C8B5Z1T', 'Golf Cart Speaker with Clamp Mount Accessories', '\"[{\"title\":\"Clear Sound and Extra Bass at its Finest\",\"text\":\"Forget about poor sound and weak bass golf cart sound bar, this portable golf cart speakers and golf cart accessories will put a smile on your face with it\\u2019s SUPER BASS and 360\\u00b0 multi-directional audio swivel. Ultra portable and easy to use, this golf cart radio and speakers will point the sound directly towards you for the ultimate on-course sound experience.\"},{\"title\":\"Play more rounds with extended battery life\",\"text\":\"Thanks to its large battery capacity, the golf cart radio kit and golf cart accessories for a club cart will stay up with you all day! 20 h battery life even during heavy use and Type C fast charging make the golf cart speakers battery one of the best features of the ezgo golf cart accessories or golf cart accessories. Don\\u2019t stop the fun\"},{\"title\":\"Sturdy Stainless Steel Bar Mount for Rough Terrain\",\"text\":\"While other golf cart stereo system have thin plastic bar mounts that do not secure the golf cart speakers on bumpy roads, this golf gifts for men speaker mount is made out of premium stainless steel that can be securely mounted on ANY GOLF club car, golf push carts or ezgo txt golf cart accessories while also protecting your golf cart radio and speakers\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions:  6.26 x 5.12 x 3.82 inches; Weight: 7 ounces; Material: Aluminum and Stainless Steel; Color: Black\"}]\"', 39.99, 'gadget', 'img5_5C8B5Z1T.png', 'https://www.BetterProtechtion.com/img/img4.jpg', 0, NULL, 0),
(5, '2C8E0U0E', 'Golf Practice Hitting Net with Turf Mat', '\"[{\"title\":\"Improve Golf Skills\",\"text\":\"Golf driving practice net is designed with a target - helps you practicing your chip shots and accuracy and provides a focal point for your driving training. ELLOLLA golf target hitting net is designed with three targets: lob, chip, running, you can practice your cutting skills according to the height of the target and different distances, for practicing your golf swing, hitting and driving in your backyard\"},{\"title\":\"Automatic Ball Return System\",\"text\":\"The ball automatically rolls back. No more bending or chasing your ball. Get more putts with less effort ultimately improving your short game. Easy ball capture. Safely swing inside or outside. The net is made of waterproof polyester fabric and wear resistant nylon. The support rod is made of fiberglass, which is light and good elasticity\"},{\"title\":\"With Turf Grass Mat\",\"text\":\"Save your lawn and your wallet with our hitting mat! The package includes hitting turf mat; practicing balls; storage bag; golf net. Exceptional portability allows you to set up the mat within seconds and is designed for both indoor and outdoor use. Never worry about weather conditions again when you want to get practice time in. Send your family or friends a Golfing Gods golf net as a perfect gift, enjoy it at the office, garden, living room and more\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 22.01 x 12.48 x 2.32 inches; Weight: 5.22 Pounds; Color: Black\"}]\"', 49.95, 'gadget', 'img5_2C8E0U0E.png', 'https://www.LifeImproveDevice.com/img/img5.jpg', 0, NULL, 0),
