(7, '4P5R7D2M', 'Hoverboard', '\"[{\"text\":\"ULTRA-FUN HOVERBOARD -  Hoverboard Scooter offers 6.5\\\" wheels for a smooth ride, 400W motors (200W x 2) delivers plenty of torque to get up inclines of up to 10 degrees. With a top speed of 7 mph over and a 6 mile range,  hoverboard offers hours of fun.\"},{\"text\":\"FUN, EASY AND INTUITIVE RIDING \\u2013 Step on one side first, the board stabilizes so you can put your other foot on. Controls are easy to learn, allowing you to smoothly accelerate\\/decelerate by applying pressure with your feet and\\/or leaning.\"},{\"text\":\"BEST SELF-BALANCING SYSTEM - With  gyroscopes and acceleration sensors, the built-in inertia dynamic stabilization system keeps you in control. Hoverboard scooter stabilizes the rider, controls balance and motion for a safe, stable & fun riding experience.\"},{\"text\":\"LONG-LASTING BATTERY - IPX-4 rated for water-resistance, this hoverboard features a built-in 25.2V\\/4.0 Ah Lithium-ion rechargeable battery (certified), fully charges in 5 hours (charger included). The safety shield battery enclosure prevents fire & overheating.\"},{\"text\":\"WE TAKE SAFETY SERIOUSLY - The hoverboard sends alerts if you are speeding or riding on unsafe surfaces so you can slow down and avoid mishaps. LED lights on both sides of the hoverboard adds visibility of any rider when it matters most.\"},{\"text\":\"FUN FOR KIDS, TEENS AND ADULTS - No matter where you\'re riding, you\'ll have fun with friends and family.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 23.75 x 9 x 8.1 inches. Weight: 7.12 Kilograms.\"}]\"', 89.95, 'gadget', 'img7_4P5R7D2M.png', 'https://www.AccessoryHomeGadget.com/img/img7.png', 0, NULL, 0),
