(2, '2B7K1C8I', 'Kitchen Scale', '\"[{\"title\":\"\",\"text\":\"A Premium Choice: Between the design and quality, this kitchen scale is going to last and function at an impeccable level. Your cooking just got ten times easier!\"},{\"title\":\"\",\"text\":\"Fresh Features: All of the qualities you need and expect in a kitchen scale: readings down to the gram, an eleven pound capacity, and easy to read display. What more could you want?\"},{\"title\":\"\",\"text\":\"Simple And Stylish: Don\\u2019t let the kitchen accessories cramp your style\\u2014the simplistic, modern design of this scale fits right in with the decor of any trendy space. Go ahead and leave it on the counter; it shows you care about your kitchen.\"}]\"', 5.95, 'gadget', 'img2_2B7K1C8I.png', 'https://www.ThePowerfulWidget.com/img/img1.png', 0, NULL, 0),
