(7, '7B6A6Q4P', 'Leg Massager', '\"[{\"text\":\"Maximize Your Foot And Calf Massage Experience: Effectively relieve fatigue and discomfort of your tired feet and lower leg. The airbag pressure on your tissue will also improve the blood circulation.\"},{\"text\":\"Customize Modes And Intensity Levels: 2 modes and 3 intensity levels provides different massage experience. You can maximize the strength of the pressure from the air bags with the touch on the air pressure button.\"},{\"text\":\"Adjustable And Flexible: One size fits all. With the use of adjustable Velcro straps, you can loosen or tighten the massage straps according to your desire or comfort, and the maximum calf circumference can be adjusted to 22.83 inches.\"},{\"text\":\"Easy To Use Controller And Comfortable Material: You can operate and customize the features with the massager\\u2019s easy to use buttons. It is made of breathable and durable material to ensure that you can comfortably and reliably use it.\"},{\"text\":\"Portable And Safe To Use: Easy to pack and use anywhere. It has a built in 20 min AUTO OFF feature to ensure that it will stop after one session. You can use it at home while watching TV or even in your office.\"}]\"', 89.95, 'gadget', 'img7_7B6A6Q4P.png', 'https://www.NewTownGadget.com/img/img7.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(8, '6S0Q0P0M', 'Leg Massager, for Circulation and Relaxing Muscles', '\"[{\"title\":\"ULTIMATE WHOLE LEG MASSAGER\",\"text\":\"Everyone may have leg issues such as soreness, stiff muscles, poor circulation, or leg fatigue with stress and sports. The compression massager for legs and feet is designed with the latest bionics technology that simulates hands kneading massage and compress muscles contraction. It brings more effective and affordable therapy compare to old massage.\"},{\"title\":\"SIMPLICITY & POWERFUL MASSAGE MODES\",\"text\":\"The leg massagers for pain and circulation come with ergonomic and powerful massage function design. It provides 4 massage modes and 4 intensities with an LCD digital controller. The new generation air compression leg massager is more friendly and easy to use for the elderly or people who need special massage demands. \"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 16.18 x 9.45 x 7.2 inches; Weight: 4.92 Pounds; Color: Black\"}]\"', 119, 'gadget', 'img8_6S0Q0P0M.png', 'https://www.ExtraFunWidget.com/img/img9.jpg', 0, NULL, 0),
