(8, '3V7V6E1H', 'Levitating Moon Lamp Night Light ', '\"[{\"title\":\"MAGNETIC LEVITATING MOON LAMP\",\"text\":\"Adopt Magnetic levitation technique,Suspended and Spinning automatically in mid-air Freely without any support or contact,it can be able to attract people\'s eyes. Adopt 3D printing technology to imitate Moon Surface to create a texture that is similar to the real moon and the base is newly idea design.\"},{\"title\":\"WIRELESS POWER TRANSMISSION\",\"text\":\"This levitating moon lamp is powered through electromagnetic induction, no need cables or built-in battery,Soft LED light, no harm to the eye, with long service life.extremely low power consumption compared with traditional lamp lights controlled by the touch button:on\\/off. \"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 6 x 6 x 6 inches; Weight: \\u200e2.44 pounds; Color: Multi-Colored; Material: \\u200eAcrylonitrile Butadiene Styrene\"}]\"', 119, 'gadget', 'img8_3V7V6E1H.png', 'https://www.PlayfulWidget.com/img/img9.jpg', 0, NULL, 0),
(5, '7N3B1S5I', 'Levitating Speaker', '\"[{\"title\":\"Super Cool Levitating Speaker\",\"text\":\"This is a multifunctional magnetic levitating Bluetooth speaker that integrates design and technology,levitating Bluetooth speaker with high-fidelity sound experience,360-degree rotation,one-touch hands-free calling,touch sensing control, colorful LED flashing lights,fashionable and trendy design makes it stand out from many ordinary Bluetooth speakers,no matter where you place it,it can be for you icing on the cake.\"},{\"title\":\"Touch Sensor Control,One-Touch Hands-Free Call\",\"text\":\"Our Orb levitating speaker is designed with touch sensor, you can adjust the volume,switch the song,control the light as you like,one key hands-free answer the phone,no need to hold the phone can be used conveniently,at the same time,the floating speaker built-in noise canceling microphone, the sound is bright and clear,so you communicate zero distance.\"},{\"title\":\"Amazing 360-Degree Rotation And Led Visual Effects\",\"text\":\"The magnetic levitation speaker uses magnetic levitation technology,when Orb speakers are floating and rotating in the air, they look really cool! The lights around the base and speakers emit a wonderful club atmosphere,These lights move along with the rhythm of the music you are playing, entertaining your eyes as your listen to wonderful music.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 3.07 x 3.07 x 3.07 inches; Weight: 2.57 pounds; Material: Aircraft Grade Aluminum; Color: Black\"}]\"', 49.95, 'gadget', 'img5_7N3B1S5I.png', 'https://www.BetterProtechtion.com/img/img5.jpg', 0, NULL, 0),
