(2, '5H6J7X6D', 'Mini Clip-on Selfie LED Ring Light', '\"[{\"text\":\"LED Light & Makeup Mirror: 2-in-1 design, combines the LED ring light and makeup mirror together, suitable for smartphone selfie photos taking, live streaming, video recording, quick touch-ups, etc.\"},{\"text\":\"Bi-color Temperature: bi-color temperature design, with 12pcs 3200K LEDs and 12pcs 5500K LEDs, providing you with more natural light and helping you take more vivid photos.\"},{\"text\":\"Adjustable Brightness: 3 lighting modes(cold light, warm light, cold + warm light), each lighting mode has 3 levels of adjustable brightness, which can meet all your needs in different circumstances.\"},{\"text\":\"Universal Phone Clip: Clip-on design, compatible with almost all smartphones, suitable for iPhone X\\/8\\/7\\/7 Plus\\/6 Plus\\/6\\/6S... for Samsung, Huawei, Xiaomi and other brands smartphone.\"},{\"text\":\"Portable & Lightweight: compact size, can be easily carried in your pocket or handbag; plastic shell, super lightweight, you can take it with you anywhere you go.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 4.65 x 4.21 x 1.42 inches. Weight: 4.3 ounces.\"}]\"', 7.95, 'gadget', 'img2_5H6J7X6D.png', 'https://www.AllYouNeedGadget.com/img/img17.png', 0, NULL, 0),
