(7, '8D1D2O0Y', 'Panoramic Head Camera Tripod', '\"[{\"title\":\"SOLID CONSTRUCTION\",\"text\":\"All-metal design, sturdy and durable, Made of aluminium alloy material, CNC precision processing, and surface adopts anti-oxidation treatment; The force of all-metal locking knobs are very strong to make sure the safety of your camera\"},{\"title\":\"COMPATIBILITY\",\"text\":\"It can be mounted on the tripod, monopod and other devices with 1\\/4 inch or 3\\/8 inch screw, or standard clamp, it is flexible and stable; QR plate with standard 1\\/4inch screw and anti-slip rubber pad, it is easy to install your camera and keep it safe (Max Load 22 Pounds) \"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 9.06 x 6.3 x 5.31 inches; Weight: 1.78 pounds; Maximum Weight Recommendation: 22 pounds; Material: Aluminium Alloy; Color: Black and Red\"}]\"', 89.95, 'gadget', 'img7_8D1D2O0Y.png', 'https://www.SignatureToolMaster.com/img/img7.jpg', 0, NULL, 0),
