(5, '7D8Z4D5M', 'Paper Trimmer', '\"[{\"text\":\"Everyday portable paper trimmer with 15-inch guillotine-style, self-sharpening steel blade; ideal for home or office.\"},{\"text\":\"Cleanly cuts up to 10 sheets of 20-pound paper at a time; sharp enough to accurately trim cardstock, construction paper, photos, and more.\"},{\"text\":\"Guardrail keeps fingers a safe distance from the blade; when not in use, trimmer arm can be secured in place, fully hiding the blade.\"},{\"text\":\"Durable plastic base with white 1\\/2-inch gridlines (0.5 by 0.5 inches) and a printed ruler (in inches and cm) that allow for reliable alignment and precision cuts.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 21.7 x 14 x 2.6 inches; Weight: 3.9 pounds; Material: Steel; Color: Black\"}]\"', 39.99, 'gadget', 'img5_7D8Z4D5M.png', 'https://www.SmartTechGearPro.com/img/img4.png', 0, NULL, 0),
