(5, '8I5R5B2Y', 'Pepper and Spice Mill', '\"[{\"text\":\"Grind sea salt, peppercorns, and dried spices at the touch of a button.\"},{\"text\":\"Charging base with charge\\/ready light and removable crumb tray.\"},{\"text\":\"Adjustable fine to coarse grind setting in one revolution.\"},{\"text\":\"Clear grinding containers let you know when to refill.\"},{\"text\":\"Package Dimensions: 4 x 6.13 x 9.75 inches. Weight: 1.25 pounds.\"}]\"', 49.95, 'gadget', 'img5_8I5R5B2Y.png', 'https://www.AllBestTechTool.com/img/img5.png', 0, NULL, 0),
