(4, '0B4U8P7Q', 'Personal Blender', '\"[{\"text\":\"Compact design and BPA free: Great for home, office and travel with on the go portability.\"},{\"text\":\"Blend and go: Blend and drink from the 14 ounce jar and lid which are both dishwasher safe.\"},{\"text\":\"One-touch blending: Makes great smoothies, shakes, baby formula, marinades, salad dressing and more. To remove stubborn spots, use a mild, non-abrasive cleanser.\"},{\"text\":\"Stainless steel blades: Ice crushing power for smooth results.\"},{\"text\":\"Efficient 175 watt motor provides all the power you need for fast, reliable performance.\"}]\"', 24.99, 'gadget', 'img4_0B4U8P7Q.png', 'https://www.GadgetProLife.com/img/img3.png', 0, NULL, 0),
