(4, '1I0V1P5H', 'Power Strip - 10 FT Long', '\"[{\"text\":\"Power Plug Type \\tType B - 3 pin (North American)\"},{\"text\":\"Color \\tWhite\"},{\"text\":\"Voltage \\t125 Volts\"},{\"text\":\"Maximum Surge Rating \\t2100 Joules\"},{\"text\":\" \\u2611\\ufe0f Power Strip Surge Protector with Wide-Spaced Outlets: This power strip has six surge protector outlets, five wide spaced and one extra wide spaced, a practical design that beats narrow ineffective socket panels. With a 10 ft. heavy-duty extension cord, the optimal length to cover your power adapters or chargers, it will satisfy all your charging needs at home and the office\"},{\"text\":\"\\u2611\\ufe0f USB Power Strip with Smart IC: The surge protector power strip with USB ports can provides a 5V\\/2.4A maximum charging current per port (share 3.4A\\/17W). With built-in smart IC (integrated circuit), it delivers optimal charging currents to your devices according to their need, perfect for simultaneously charging cellphones, laptops, tablets and cameras without a variety of converters. The three-prong power strip flat plug takes up little space, so you can keep your desktop organized\"},{\"text\":\"\\u2611\\ufe0f Outlet Surge Protector with Overload Protection: Safeguard your computer, TV and refrigerator. Built-in 2100 J surge-suppression MOV(metal oxide varistor) protects your electrical appliances from lightning, power surges and spikes. The illuminated power switch with a 10A circuit breaker signifies your devices are protected from power surges, over-heating, overload and over-charging\"},{\"text\":\"\\u2611\\ufe0f 10 ft. Cord Surge Protector and Right Angle Power Strip: The 10 ft. ETL Listed extension cord is made from 18 AWG pure copper, which is very thick and has better current-carrying capacity. The 45\\u00b0 flat plug will not block the bottom receptacle of your duplex wall outlet. Two back holes allow you to install the power strips on the wall and in the workshop \"},{\"text\":\"\\u3010POWER STRIP WITH USB\\u3011 - The usb power strip with 6 ac outlets and 3 usb, build in smart charging technology, the USB charger will detect your devices automatically and deliver the fastest charge speed up to 2.4A ( 5V\\/2.4 Max Each Port ), 3 USB ports ( Total 5V\\/3.1A\\/15W) can charge almost any USB device (smart phone, tablet, Amazon Kindle, fire stick, e-reader, blue tooth headphones, portable speaker etc) .\"},{\"text\":\"\\u3010UPGRADED UL APPROVAL CORD\\u3011 - 10 FT extra long heavy duty cord with accredited by UL. The power cord housed in a durable braided insulation and jacket with a space-saving flat plug to allow unit to fit closely to the wall. Fire-resistance PC shell with flame retardant at 1382\\u2109 makes it more durable and more secure, 100% great heat dissipation copper wire (over 10000 times pull and plug), special Phosphor copper conductor for socket.\"},{\"text\":\"\\u3010ON\\/OFF SWITCH\\u3011 - The white power strip built-in multiple security module safeguards your expensive computers, tv and all other electronic devices from overload, short circuit, voltage fluctuations. the reliable overload switch will trip off automatically to protect your devices and your home when the power overload. The small indicator light lets you know the power is active while does not cause bright light in the dark.\"},{\"text\":\"\\u3010RIGHT ANGLE FLAT PLUG & WALL MOUNTABLE \\u3011- The flat plug features a low profile fits easily in tight spaces, the two mounting holes and 10 ft long cord, allows this wall mount power strip to be securely installed in various applications, such as workbenches, wallmounts, floormounts, under counters & more.\"}]\"', 24.99, 'gadget', 'img4_1I0V1P5H.png', 'https://www.PremiumDailyDevice.com/img/img3.jpg', 0, NULL, 0),
(4, '1T1L2Y3W', 'Power Strip Surge Protector', '\"[{\"title\":\"Multi-Outlet Surge Protector Power Strip\",\"text\":\"Power everything on your desk with a single compact surge-protected extension cord. This reputable power cord offers 12 AC outlets with surge protector for charging your computer, laptop, phone, camera, and more. One charging station for a clutter-free desk.\"},{\"title\":\"Power Bar with Phone Line Protection\",\"text\":\"Featuring a 1-in-2-out RJ11 telephone or fax protection to ensure open and continuous phone line connections. It also provides a coaxial cable protection to safeguard cable box and satellite connections. The damage-resistant housing protects circuits from fire, impact, and rust.\"},{\"title\":\"Safeguard Your Devices and Appliances\",\"text\":\"The electric strip has a 3,940-Joule energy rating providing a reliable power extension cord to protect printers, broadband modems, or home theater systems. It secures your electronic devices from overload, short circuit, power spikes, lightning strikes, or fluctuations.\"},{\"title\":\"Compact, Heavy Duty, and Space-Saving\",\"text\":\"The widely spaced outlets give ample area to fit big plugs and charger bricks. Its slender design makes it ideal for home office, workstations, and game rooms. The durable cord is 8 ft \\/ 2.4 meters long with a 3-prong angle plug convenient for tight spaces.\"},{\"title\":\"Reliable Product and Service\",\"text\":\"Purchase with confidence as it is backed by a limited lifetime warranty and protected by a dollar 200,000 Connected Equipment Warranty. Check out the full specs: 6,000 volts maximum spike voltage, 15A AC, 125V, and 1875W. Each outlet has a safety slide lock to close unused sockets safeguarding you and your kids.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 6.1 x 2.1 x 15.6 inches; Weight: 2 Pounds; Material: MOV; Color: Gray\"}]\"', 24.99, 'gadget', 'img4_1T1L2Y3W.png', 'https://www.NewTechNewGadget.com/img/img3.png', 0, NULL, 0);
