(6, '6D8D4K0Z', 'Vacuum Seal System', '\"[{\"text\":\"Vacuum sealer appliance with selectable modes for wet or dry food.\"},{\"text\":\"Effectively vacuum seal pre-made meals, produce, meat, dry goods, and more for preservation and freshness.\"},{\"text\":\"Safely preserves frozen meat up to 3 years and refrigerated items for weeks.\"},{\"text\":\"Includes air suction hose and 16 foot roller bag; LED process indicator lights.\"},{\"text\":\"Built-in cutter creates custom bag sizes for easy storage and waste reduction.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 15.04 x 4.09 x 2.44 inches; Weight: 37.04 Ounces; Material: Stainless Steel; Color: White\"}]\"', 69.99, 'gadget', 'img6_6D8D4K0Z.png', 'https://www.ProTechDeviceLover.com/img/img6.png', 0, NULL, 0),
