(9, '1V8K2R7D', 'Vacuum Sealer Machine System', '\"[{\"text\":\" Food preserved with the FoodSaver System in the freezer can last up to 3 years and still taste fresh, flavorful, and freezer-burn free. Prep-ahead meals, leftovers, and produce stored in the fridge will stay fresh up to weeks later instead of spoiling in days.\"},{\"text\":\"Designed to minimize bag waste compared to previous FoodSaver models; features a built-in roll cutter so you can create custom-sized bags without using scissors.\"},{\"text\":\"Equipped with dual heat sealing strips, it\'s guaranteed to reach an optimal vacuum level and airtight seal. The FM2100 is durable, high quality, and backed by a 5-year limited warranty.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 17.8 x 5.9 x 13.3 inches; Weight: 6.6 Pounds; Color: Black; Material: Plastic\"}]\"', 132, 'gadget', 'img9_1V8K2R7D.png', 'https://www.TomorrowlandDevice.com/img/img18.png', 0, NULL, 0),
