(10, '8J2V8R6C', 'eReader', '\"[{\"title\":\"Adjustable Birghtness & Blue Light Control\",\"text\":\"The eReader has ComfortLight PRO to adjust the brightness and colour temperature of your screen. Gradually reducing blue light exposure, making reading easier by limiting eyestrain, so you can read before bed in the dark comfortably.\"},{\"title\":\"Glare-Free Touchscreen\",\"text\":\"It has a natural, print-like reading experience on its 6\\\" high-definition 300PPI screen. Unlike your tablet or smartphone, this eReader has a screen that is glare-free so you can read in direct sunlight, just like real paper.\"},{\"title\":\"Carry Up Tp 6000 Books\",\"text\":\"With 8GB of storage take your entire book collection everywhere you go. Browse over 6 million titles at any time.\"},{\"title\":\"A Customized Reading Experience\",\"text\":\"Easily customizable features help you read the way you want to. Choose from over 50 font sizes and 12 font types. With adjustable margins, the ability to highlight passages, write notes, and a built-in dictionary at the tap of a finger, the possibilities are endless.\"},{\"title\":\"Long Lasting Battery Life\",\"text\":\"The eReader has a battery life that lasts for weeks*, so you can experience uninterrupted reading on a single charge. *Dependent on individual usage.\"}]\"', 149, 'gadget', 'img10_8J2V8R6C.png', 'https://www.SuccessProWidget.com/img/img13.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(2, '1O7Z4T2H', 'iPhone Aux Cord for Car', '\"[{\"text\":\"Connector Type \\tAuxiliary, USB Type C\"},{\"text\":\"Cable Type \\tAUX, Lightning\"},{\"text\":\"Compatible Devices \\tPersonal Computer, Smartphone, Speaker\"},{\"text\":\"Color \\tWhite\"},{\"text\":\" \\u3010Excellent Compatibility\\u3011 Perfect Design for iPhone\\/iPod\\/iPad. This iPhone aux cable easily enable you to connect your iPhone to your car stereo, headphone, Hi-Fi, computer stereo, Bluetooth speaker or any devices equipped with standard 3.5mm audio jack aux port.\"},{\"text\":\"\\u3010Impressive Sound Transmission\\u3011 The lightning to aux cord is built with certified chip to ensure the stability and fidelity of sound transmission, giving you a fantastic music trip and experience when using this aux cord.\"},{\"text\":\"\\u3010Premium Quality Material\\u3011 The lightning to 3.5mm cable is made of high-quality textured aluminum connector, gold-plated 3.5mm conductor and durable stretch TPE material, makes the lighting aux cord to be strong but flexible, fast and sturdy connection, protect it from breaking, 100% durable to use. \"},{\"text\":\"Its lightning to 3.5mm car audio cables are certified by Apple to meet rigid iPhone requirements and ensures completely and securely connect with your Apple devices. This aux cable can easy to connect your Apple Devices to car stereos, home stereos, portable speaker, headphone, Hi-Fi, computer or anything else with a 3.5mm input jack.\"},{\"text\":\"\\u3010Compatible Device\\u3011 The lightning car audio cables are compatible with Apple iPhone 13\\/13 Pro\\/13 Pro Max\\/13 Mini\\/12\\/12 Pro\\/SE\\/11 Pro Max\\/11 Pro\\/11\\/XS\\/XS Max\\/XR\\/X\\/8\\/8 Plus\\/7\\/7 Plus and so on. Supports iOS 15\\/14\\/13\\/12\\/11\\/10 and earlier Operation System.\"},{\"text\":\"\\u3010High Performance\\u3011 The aux stereo audio cable builts with textured aluminum head and premium TPE and PVC cable material, make the audio cable to be more strong but flexible and easily survive everyday heavy usage. 100% durable to use. It\'s also light weight and convenient to take around. No worry about the winding, knot or kink.\"},{\"text\":\"\\u3010Plug and Play\\u3011 No need any driver or external power, just plug and play. Easy to connect and use. The aux cord for iPhone 12 allows you to enjoy high quality music anytime and anywhere. Great for home & travel.\"}]\"', 5.95, 'gadget', 'img2_1O7Z4T2H.png', 'https://www.PremiumDailyDevice.com/img/img1.jpg', 0, NULL, 0),
(6, '7N8X2J0U', 'mini Drone Optical Flow Positioning RC Quadcopter with 720P HD Camera', '\"[{\"text\":\"Color \\tBlack\"},{\"text\":\"Mirror Adjustment \\tRemote Control\"},{\"text\":\"Video Capture Resolution \\tFHD 1080p\"},{\"text\":\"Are Batteries Included \\tYes\"},{\"text\":\"Item Weight \\t7.04 Ounces\"},{\"text\":\"Battery Capacity \\t650 Milliamp Hours\"},{\"text\":\"Video Output Resolution \\t1920x1080 Pixels\"},{\"text\":\"Remote Control Included? \\tYes\"},{\"text\":\" Excellent Visual Experience: Compared with 720p cameras, the FPV mini drone\\u2019s 1080p HD camera enables having more stunning and crystal clearer aerial videos and photos and you can share them to your social network immediately.\"},{\"text\":\"Multiple Modes to Play Easy & Safe: The one key taking off\\/landing, headless mode, and altitude hold features, G-sensor, and 3-speed settings make operations easier and ensure a safer and smoother flight experience. Operating this mini-RC quadcopter drone is fun, safe, easy for kids and adults.\"},{\"text\":\"Foldable, Light and Easy to Carry: Weighing less than 0.44lbs, the mini foldable drone\\u2019s unfolded size is 3.93 x 4.92 x 1.18inch and its folded size is 3.15 x 2.51 x 1.18inch. Easily carry it everywhere you go with its included travel carry case.\"},{\"text\":\"Trajectory Flight & 360 Degree Flip: Simply draw a flight path on the app control interface, the mini foldable drone with camera for adults and kids will automatically fly along the trajectory. Feeling a bit daring? Try out the 360-degree flip function and watch a spectacular aerial maneuver. \"},{\"text\":\"Optical Flow Positioning and Altitude Hold . Is extremely user-friendly that comes with Optical Flow Positioning and Altitude Hold. The feature of Optical flow allows the drone to hold its position without a pilot\\u2019s maneuvering,which conduces to more stable hovering and ensures your clear photograph.One key take off\\/landing function adapts to all experience levels even for beginners.\"},{\"text\":\"Considerate Design and Easy to Carry. A battery can support up 8 to 12 mins play for each charge which grants more enough time to perform a perfect fly. Also, provides perfect solution for indoor and outdoor flying, foldable and lightweight makes it exceptionally easy to carry. Bring it anywhere, saves the space with folding size: 110*80*35mm.\"},{\"text\":\"720P Pictures & Live Videos Function. Upgrade dual camera, switch the camera of view arbitrarily which captures high-quality video and clear aerial photos.you can see what your drone sees from smartphone, enjoy a live video feed up from far away .Phone direct control with transmission which compatible with Apple IOS \\/ Android phones .\"},{\"text\":\"Headless Security Mode. Once the fuselage direction can not be recognized, it can enter headless mode so as to continue the flight.The pilot can fly the drone to any location without worrying about which direction the drone is facing. Help to prevent from losing the direction.\"}]\"', 69.99, 'gadget', 'img6_7N8X2J0U.png', 'https://www.PremiumDailyDevice.com/img/img6.jpg', 0, NULL, 0),
