(4, '5P3U8G3I', 'Anti-Theft Device', '\"[{\"text\":\"Adaptable & Impenetrable: This steering wheel lock is adjustable and fits for any car which inner diameter of steering wheel is 6.6-12.5 inches. Universal fit for cars, trucks, vans, and SUVs.\"},{\"text\":\"Keys Cannot Be Duplicated\\uff1aIt comes with 3 keys. Every lock has its individual key. Others who bought the same product can not get into your car or use it.\"},{\"text\":\"Special Design: This lock uses high quality steel which will never rust. The felt pads that stick to the metal \\\"U\\\" will not hurt the steering wheel. The sharp cone(with a protective cap) at the end of the lock can be used to escape in an emergency.\"},{\"text\":\"Easy Use: You could lock or unlock it within 5s. It can greatly save your valuable time.\"},{\"text\":\"What You Get: Steering wheel lock, 3 keys, protective cap, blue fixing velcro, 2 inner layer pads, our worry-free 12-month warranty, and friendly customer service. If you have any concerns, please do not hesitate to contact us, we are always here to help you solve them.\"}]\"', 24.99, 'auto', 'img4_5P3U8G3I.png', 'https://www.SuperFastAutomobile.com/img/img3.png', 0, NULL, 0),
