(10, '0Z1R2P3N', 'Backup Camera for Trucks', '\"[{\"text\":\"Wireless Design for Easy Installation - No More Complex Wiring Problem.  7\'\' TFT rear view monitor connects a backup camera by a wireless transmitter.You just need to connect the monitor to the lighter charger, connect the camera to running light or reversing light and you are good to go. No more complicated long video cables from the monitor to the camera. Make all things much easier.\"},{\"text\":\"Stable and Vivid HD1080P Image \\u2013With digital wireless transmission , delivers a stable image without any interference from other signals such as Bluetooth. Equipped with great sensor, the camera provides vivid picture , which restores what you see behind your car directly.V29 wireless backup camera system is with a built-in wide voltage range within 12V-35V for more vehicle models, and voltage can be adjusted by the circuit board on extension cable to greatly extend the service life 4-5 years.\"},{\"text\":\"Ideal Camera \\u2013 The waterproof standard of this camera is IP69 , the highest and lowest temperature resistance is -4\\u00b0F~149\\u00b0F, and the lumen rating is 0.1 at low light night. Therefore whether it is sunny or rainy, hot or cold, day or night, the camera always performs well.\"},{\"text\":\"Parking Safely & Effortlessly \\u2013 With Wireless Backup Camera Kit,you will be able to easily park your car even in the tiniest parking spots.Without risking damaging it and ruining your day or night! There is no battery in the backup camera,it will be safer.\"}]\"', 149, 'auto', 'img10_0Z1R2P3N.png', 'https://www.RacingSportAutomobile.com/img/img13.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(10, '8X5S0A8A', 'Bar Car Roof Rack', '\"[{\"text\":\"Heavy Duty Construction: The racks are made of 22mm diameter and 1.5mm thick steel tube, 8.5 \\\"widening design, stronger than else. Black Powder-Coated Steel for Durability & Rust Prevention Plus Long-Lasting, can resist all weather condition and use for a long life.150 Lbs Tested, easy and safe for your transport.\"},{\"text\":\"Folding And Ergonomic Design: Ergonomic quick release design, more easily to fold and raise the racks than others. Racks can be folded flat when not in use, get better clearance to drive your car into garage and not have to remove.\"},{\"text\":\"Reduce Scratch Design: Foam Padding and Rubber Pedal design to reduce scratch of your kayak and prevent the canoe or kayak from rubbing.\"},{\"text\":\"Universal Mounting Design: Compatible with most crossbars,such as square, factory and aerodynamic crossbars\\uff0cExcept the round bar.\"},{\"text\":\"Multi Purpose Use: Easy to Install, use this car roof rack to carry Kayak, Canoe, Surf board, Ski board, Snow Board and SUP. Extra 4 pcs tie down straps including.\"}]\"', 141, 'auto', 'img10_8X5S0A8A.png', 'https://www.AutomobileIngenious.com/img/img12.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(6, '8P1W1E0F', 'Battery Jump Starter', '\"[{\"text\":\"This car jump starter has enough power (2500A peak current) to jump start most 12 volt vehicles on the road! (up to 8.0L gas or 8L diesel engines) Works with cars, motorcycles, watercraft, ATVs, UTVs, SUVs, lawnmowers, yachts, boat, pickup, snowmobiles, etc. Fully charges approx 6 hours. By turning off the main switch, our battery starter can hold a charge for more than 3 months.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 8.6 x 5.1 x 3.9 inches; Voltage: 12 Volts; Vehicle Service Type: Car, Truck, UTV, Motorcycle, Dirt Bike, Personal Watercraft, RV or tractor; Color: Multicolor\"}]\"', 69.99, 'auto', 'img6_8P1W1E0F.png', 'https://www.RacingAutoClub.com/img/img6.png', 0, NULL, 0),
