(4, '7G2Q5Q3Y', 'Car Charger Adapter', '\"[{\"text\":\"PD3.0 & PPS Quick Charge: Compatible with multiple fast charging protocols such as PPS, QC3.0, PD 3.0, QC 2.0, SCP, FCP, and PE+. 5X faster than standard 5V\\/2.4A chargers. Charge your laptop from 0 to 100% in only 2 hours; Charge iPhone\\/Samsung phones from 0% to 50% within 30 minutes.\\uff08Note\\uff1aDoes not support samsung 45W phones).\"},{\"text\":\"65W Car Charger for Laptop: The type-C port of this usb c car charger supports 65W Max when another USB -A port is free. which means that you can charge your laptop\\/macbook in car when you are on bussiness\\/long travel trip. When this macbook\\/samsung\\/iPad Pro car charger rapid charging for 2 devices simultaneously, USB-A port output 18W while the USB C Port output 45W. (Note: Only support 45W Max on 12-15V cars, and 65W can be supported on cars above 20V, such as limousines, RV cars, trucks).\"},{\"text\":\"Superior Safety & Voltage Detector: Monitor the vehicle\'s electrical system and display car voltage on the screen to keep you informed of the car\'s health. Charging will be automatically stop when battery is full. The 65W fast usb c car charger built in intelligent circuit design protects against short circuiting, over-heating, over-current and over-charging. Strictly CE certification, premium construction with durable housing as well as over-charging, over-heating and short circuit protection.\"},{\"text\":\"Metal Charger with LED Display: Upgrade metal usb c car charger will not be burnt-out, certified by multiple safety certification, which is safer than plastic one. Excellent design of the soft LED light makes it effortless to find the charging port in the dark. The advanced full aluminum alloy body features scratch resistant will keep it sturdy. You might think that metal shell are more prone to heat, which actually proves that metal bodies do a good job of dissipating heat.\"},{\"text\":\"Broad Compatibility: Universal fast car charger works