(4, '2X8B7K0L', 'Car Cigarette Lighter Splitter', '\"[{\"text\":\"Cigarette Lighter Splitter Adapter - Splits 1 car cigarette lighter port to 2 DC ports, 1 cigarette lighter male plug to 2 female sockets. A 2-Way cigarette lighter splitter adapter extension cord allows you to connect two of your 12 volt devices at the same time. Cable Length: 10 inch\\/25 cm.\"},{\"text\":\"Multiple Safety Protection - This heavy-duty cigarette lighter extension cable uses SPT-2 16AWG pure copper UL Certified Wire to provide stable current for your devices. Double PVC jacket, best insulation effect, 105 \\u00b0C heat resistance. Male plug built-in replaceable 15A safe fuse, timely cut off the current to prevent the car splitter and your devices from over-current, over-voltage, over-load, over-heating and short-circuit.\"},{\"text\":\"Durable Easy To Use - Plug and play, easy to use without any installation. There is a power indicator light on the male plug that allows you to check the connection status at any time and find it easily in the dark. Upgraded anti-slip flat spring to ensure a tight connection and not easy to slide out. Metal-reinforced female sockets and heavy-duty wire are reliable year after year.\"},{\"text\":\"Wide Application - This cigarette lighter adapter doubles the car\'s power port. Two 12V\\/24V cigarette lighter sockets perfectly fit for your GPS, dash cam, seat heater, car refrigerator, vacuum cleaner, air purifier and other car products. Widely used in car, RV, truck, boat, travel trailer, pickup, van while traveling. Meet your needs for more car cigarette lighter power ports.\"},{\"text\":\"Package Included - Package includes 1 x Cigarette Lighter 2-Way Splitter , 1 x 15A Fuse(built in the male plug).\"},{\"text\":\"Package Dimensions: 6 x 3 x 1.3 inches. Weight: 0.8 ounces.\"}]\"', 24.99, 'auto', 'img4_2X8B7K0L.png', 'https://www.AutoGearNation.com/img/img3.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(4, '8A2U0S6D', 'Car Cleaning Gun', '\"[{\"text\":\"Air Cleaning Tool - Widely used for cleaning leather car upholstery, dashboard, steering wheel, door panels, carpet, floor mats,the engine surface, seats, meters, door panels, roofs, interiors and so on.\"},{\"text\":\"Many Uses - Car cleaning guns are suitable for cleaning the interior of cars, such as car roofs, steering wheels, center consoles, seats and carpets, especially for gaps. It has three types of brush heads, namely a horn, a plastic brush head and an alloy brush head, which you can choose according to your needs.\"},{\"text\":\"High Quality - The car cleaning gun tool is made of high quality aluminum alloy material and is very environmentally friendly. The aluminum alloy material is strengthened by heat treatment and alloying, and its strength is greatly increased. It is easy to regenerate and is also pollution-free during disposal, which is good for environmental protection. This material has a dense oxide film on the surface that prevents corrosion and is therefore extremely durable.\"},{\"text\":\"Ergonomic - The handle of the car cleaning gun is ergonomically designed for comfortable grip. It adopts the trigger type air volume control valve, which can be started by one button. It can control the air volume at the same time, and the air supply is stable.\"}]\"', 24.99, 'auto', 'img4_8A2U0S6D.png', 'https://www.LoyalAutoPartsCenter.com/img/img3.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(4, '3M6T4I3K', 'Car Cleaning Tools Kit', '\"[{\"text\":\"Car Cleaning Tools Kit: 18 pcs car cleaning tools kit includes 5 detailing brushes, 4 drill brush attachment,3 wire brushes, 2 air outlet brush, 2 microfiber wax applicator, 1 car wash mitt,1pc towels,for you to clean the interior and exterior of the auto.\"},{\"text\":\"Detailing Brush Set: 5 different sizes detailing brush set are available for any cleaning needs.The smaller detailing brush can get into all the little cracks, the nooks, the lug nuts or tight space. The lager detailing brush suit for cleaning exterior and wider area more efficiently. Such as wheels, air vent, car seats, engine bay, dashboard, emblems and so on.\"},{\"text\":\"Drill Brush Attachment Set: 4 pcs essential power scrubber attachments for washing automotive exterior and interior surfaces . Drill brush attachment kit can also allows you to clean faster and easier in the bathroom, kitchen, and outdoor marine applications. Nylon bristles without wire will not scratch tile\\/grout, porcelain, wood, linoleum, plastic.(Cordless Drill NOT included).\"},{\"text\":\"Wire Brush Set: 3 pcs wire brush set includes 1 steel stainless brush, 1 brass brush and 1 nylon brush.Suitable for different surface types, they will address all your cleaning concerns.You can use the stainless steel wire brush for rust removal, while the nylon brush is perfect for clean delicate household appliances. The brass brush is ideal to clean metal surfaces without scratching them.\"},{\"text\":\"Widely Used: 18 pcs car cleaning kit apply to cars, trucks, motorcycles, bicycles, RVs, boats, wheels, tire, rims, spokes, grills, engine bays, exhaust tips, bumpers, inner fender, undercarriage, vents etc,it can be a great gift that keeps on giving for any car buffs, truck enthusiasts or classic car fan.\"}]\"', 24.99, 'auto', 'img4_3M6T4I3K.png', 'https://www.AutomobileRacingPro.com/img/img3.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(5, '0H0T4P4I', 'Car Coat Hanger', '\"[{\"text\":\"Our car coat holder has Design Patent. Luxury out looking blends suitably with your car\\u2019s interior. High quality and good design of our car coat hanger is in line with international standards. Our high-quality car coat hanger have been continuously proved.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: \\u200e19.41 x 9.69 x 3.54 inches; Weight: 2.18 pounds; Material: Plastic; Color: Black\"}]\"', 39.99, 'auto', 'img5_0H0T4P4I.png', 'https://www.SuperPartsZone.com/img/img4.png', 0, NULL, 0),
