(5, '2G5I6H5L', 'Foam Cannon', '\"[{\"text\":\"Heavy Duty Carwash Foam Cannon \\u2013 Pressure washer soap cannon connects to any pressure washer to deliver extreme wash foam. Super foam washes away dirt on cars, trucks, RVs, ATV, off road vehicles, household, driveways, patios, decks, and much more. Works with your favorite car wash soap. Makes washing your car faster and easier. Quality designed for detailing jobs. Generates thick foam suds to clean away road filth and dirt. Perfect for fast cleaning of cars.\"},{\"text\":\"Works With All Pressure Washers \\u2013 Professional foam cannon connects to all gas and electric pressure washers. Max rating of 4,000PSI for extreme durability. Simply connect to any pressure washer and add car wash soap for mega foam suds. Hose water is pressurized by washer for extreme foam wash. Breaks loose dirt, filth, and stains from exterior surfaces. Foam lance makes washing your vehicle easy. The best water cannon pressure washer for your detailing.\"},{\"text\":\"Easy To Use Design \\u2013 Car wash bottle sprayer features wide mouth design and connect to your pressure washer. Dual-bottle innovation connects to wide and standard foam cannon bottles. Fully adjustable controls give the perfect foam setting for detailing your vehicle. Wide fan adjustment covers full area for fast washing and control. Injector System creates extreme soap foam. Ergonomic design increases comfort while washing any car.\"},{\"text\":\"Cleans Away Dirt And Grime \\u2013 Car wash soap cannon cleans away heavy dirt and grime. Reduces swirls and scratches when washing to maintain showroom shine. Snow foam cannon is the best tool attachment for your home pressure washer system. Rinse your driveway, deck, or patio for a clean home. Professional foam lance works with all soaps and cleaning chemicals.\"},{\"text\":\"Ready To Work \\u2013 Foaming pressure washer attachment is built for any cleaning job. High pressure foam stream cleans and rinses away all dirt and grease. Auto detailing cannon washer makes washing big vehicles easy. The perfect attachment for drivers who love their cars. Powerful soap cannon safely blasts away bird droppings, mud, leaves, and much more. Soap dispenser is fast and effective.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 10.2 x 6.38 x 5.28 inches. Weight: 1.17 pounds.\"}]\"', 39.99, 'auto', 'img5_2G5I6H5L.png', 'https://www.SuperFastAutoGearPro.com/img/img4.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(4, '5B7A5A1W', 'Foam Gun', '\"[{\"text\":\"Easy To Use - just fill up the reservoir bottle with soap, click in to your existing pressure washer lance or trigger, adjust the knob for your desired foam level, and spray! Hose water from compressor comes quick for a cleaner advanced automotive dirt removal.\"},{\"text\":\"Great For Car Washing - Soak your ride in a mountain of suds to ensure that all the grime, bugs, dirt, sap, dust, and other contaminants from the road are loose before you try to wipe them off. Professional attachments and accessories for guys who love cars.\"},{\"text\":\"Wide Neck Won\'T Crack - Scroll through the images of all the generic canons, you\'ll see a common theme: Cracked necks. Our design has an extra-wide neck to prevent that problem. This canon works for car washing but can also help to clean off the side of your home, your sidewalk, or anything else that needs a deep cleaning. Works with any psi sprayer, the perfect foaming tool for any detergent.\"}]\"', 24.99, 'auto', 'img4_5B7A5A1W.png', 'https://www.SpeedAutomobileUnion.com/img/img3.png', 0, NULL, 0),
