(9, '7Z8V6J7L', 'GPS Navigator System', '\"[{\"text\":\"Driver Alerts: Receive alerts for upcoming sharp curves, speed changes, school zones, a fatigue warning, nearby red light and speed cameras and more.\"},{\"text\":\"Easy To Use: Dedicated GPS navigators display current street, current speed, speed limit and arrival time.\"},{\"text\":\"Real Directions: Guides like a friend, using recognizable landmarks, buildings and traffic lights; Display type : WQVGA color TFT with white back light.\"},{\"text\":\"Foursquare: Pre loaded data from Foursquare adds millions of new and popular stores, restaurants and more; Display resolution 480 x 272 pixels.\"},{\"text\":\"Direct Access Simplifies navigating to select complex destinations, such as malls and airports ; rechargeable lithium ion. Battery life up to 1 hour.\"},{\"text\":\"Free lifetime traffic avoidance for a stress free driving. Display size : 4.4 W x 2.5 H inch (11.1 x 6.3 cm).\"},{\"text\":\"This USB mass storage device is compatible with Windows XP or newer and Mac OS X 10.4 or later.\"}]\"', 129.87, 'auto', 'img9_7Z8V6J7L.png', 'https://www.LoyalAutoPartsCenter.com/img/img13.png', 0, NULL, 0),
