(9, '5E5H1O6C', 'Wireless Backup Camera', '\"[{\"text\":\"Works with your compatible wi-fi enabled navigator to see what\\u2019s behind your vehicle.\"},{\"text\":\"Installs quickly and easily by snapping into the included license plate mount.\"},{\"text\":\"Wirelessly pairs with a compatible Wi-Fi enabled navigator to see the backup camera view on the navigation display.\"},{\"text\":\"Transmits data up to 25\\u2019 to provide a wide, clear video image of what\\u2019s behind your vehicle.\"},{\"text\":\"Rugged and weatherproof water-rated to IPX7 (splashes, rain or snow) to withstand various road conditions.\"},{\"text\":\"Voice commands can initiate the BC 40 camera view.\"},{\"text\":\"Uses 2 AA batteries; battery life lasts up to 3 months with average use (lithium recommended, sold separately).\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 10.2 x 6.6 x 2.7 inches. Weight: 2.08 ounces.\"}]\"', 129.87, 'auto', 'img9_5E5H1O6C.png', 'https://www.SuperFastAutoGearPro.com/img/img13.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(10, '7C5K4S5A', 'Wireless Backup Camera Kit', '\"[{\"text\":\"Stable Digital Wireless Signal: Uses digital wireless signal, so you can view your rear blind spot without interference and flicker. The wireless range (33ft) is wide enough to make it work with a range of everyday vehicles.\"},{\"text\":\"Clear, High-Quality Images: 5\\u2033 TFT-LCD screen has enough detail, contrast and color accuracy to distinguish objects, which helps details pop. The images on the screen are clear and readable, so you know you are safely reversing.\"},{\"text\":\"Easier Installation: Uses digital wireless technology to transmit the signal between the monitor and camera. Thus you don\\u2019t have to run cables from front to rear which is much annoying parts of wiring. It would save your time and make the wiring much more simple.\"},{\"text\":\"Adjustable Reverse Camera: You can choose the guideline and adjust the angle of the camera up or down to suit your vehicle. As the same guideline and angle aren\\u2019t ideal for both a low-to-the-ground sedan and a taller SUV.\"},{\"text\":\"Good low-light Vision: Even with only the reverse lights, the obstacle behind the car can\'t escape your eyes. Illumination can be as low as 0.1LUX (For your reference, a night with a full moon is rated at around 0.1 Lux while sunny day rated at around 10,000 Lux). \"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 4.5 x 0.5 x 3.4 inches; Screen Size: 4.3 inches; Weight: \\u200e1.1 pounds; Color: Black\"}]\"', 149, 'auto', 'img10_7C5K4S5A.png', 'https://www.SpeedAutomobileNation.com/img/img13.png', 0, NULL, 0),
