(5, '5O1T1Y8R', 'Wireless Charging Car', '\"[{\"text\":\"Slim & Elegant Profile: Unibody aluminum housing for superior strength and a more compact design.\"},{\"text\":\"Powerful Magnetic Hold: Your compatible iPhones and cases will be held securely in place even on rough roads. Additional vertical magnet provides even stronger grip and easy alignment.\"},{\"text\":\"Wireless Charging: A  iPhone accessory designed for the technology of the future. Delivers up to 7.5W of power to compatible iPhones. USB-C car charger included.\"},{\"text\":\"Easy Installation: Silicone prongs provide a vice-like grip, and allow the mount to be installed quickly and securely. (see photo for details).\"},{\"text\":\"Functional Design: Air vent mount is made with an aluminum housing for more efficient heat dissipation than traditional materials, allowing any  iPhone to charge with maximum efficiency.\"}]\"', 49.95, 'auto', 'img5_5O1T1Y8R.png', 'https://www.SuperFastAutomobile.com/img/img5.png', 0, NULL, 0),
