(2, '3Y6D3Z4R', 'Bird Mirror Toy', '\"[{\"text\":\"SUITABLE BIRDS: These bird mirror toy is suitable for small and medium parrots, such as parakeet, cockatiel, conure, lovebird, finch, lorikeet, african grey, canary, cockatoo and so on.\"},{\"text\":\"SINGLE MIRROR DESIGN: These bird mirror toys are one-sided, it ensures that the mirror only faces inside the cage towards the bird and does\\u2019 t cause any unnecessary distractions to the others in the household.\"},{\"text\":\"EASY INSTALL & DURABLE: These bird mirror toys with sturdy stainless steel chain link and hook design, you can easily hang the mirror in the cage, it is not easy to break, it will not be easily damaged by birds, and it will not cause damage to birds.\"},{\"text\":\"STAY HEALTHY: Mirror design, sweet sounds can satisfy pets\' curiosity and attract their attention, encourage them to interact with themselves in the mirror to keep them busy for a long time and do more exercise, keep them happy for a long time and stay healthy.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 3.98 x 3.94 x 1.06 inches. Weight: 0.63 Ounces.\"}]\"', 7.95, 'pet', 'img2_3Y6D3Z4R.png', 'https://www.CutiePiePetStore.com/img/img17.png', 0, NULL, 0),
