(10, '7H6X4A8S', 'Carrier Backpack for Small Pets', '\"[{\"text\":\"A backpack with plenty of room? Check. Laptop and iPad sleeve? Check. And a carrier for your dog? We\\u2019re just getting started. Meet our carrier backpack, a stylish solution to carrying your little pooch around without needing to worry about their safety. With a waterproof bottom, padded back for comfort, and top\\/side ventilation, you\\u2019ll go everywhere together. We\\u2019ve even included a sternum strap for extra support and top buckles that are also bottle openers. Simply secure the interior tether on your dog\\u2019s harness, and you\\u2019re off!\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 16.89 x 12.95 x 4.65 inches; Weight: 4.19 pounds; Color: Light Brown;\"}]\"', 141, 'pet', 'img10_7H6X4A8S.png', 'https://www.LittlePawsPetStore.com/img/img12.jpg', 0, NULL, 0),
