(3, '2W1L7Y8S', 'Cat Bowl', '\"[{\"text\":\"Less Vomiting: the elevated cat bowl put a cat\'s mouth at a suitable position in relation to its stomach, it helps cat swallow more easily and alleviates their occasional vomiting.\"},{\"text\":\"Tilt Angle Design: 5 inches in width, the tilted cat food bowl keeps food piled or falls to the center, it helps keep the food from being pushed off the bowl, easy for your cat to eat. Perfect for flat face cats.\"},{\"text\":\"Reduce Neck Burden: the raised cat bowl has the right height, (tilt angle design, minimum height: 2 inches, maximum height: 3.6 inches) allowing the cat to eat in a more natural neck position. So your cat could sit and eat quite comfortably.\"},{\"text\":\"Less Mess and Happy Owner: the stable base is wider, it makes for secure eating without the mess of tipping over. Cutting down drastically on making a mess.\"},{\"text\":\"Sturdy Ceramic: Microwave and Dishwasher safe. Cat owners can appreciate the convenience of tossing the ceramic cat bowl into the dishwasher and flipping on the switch.\"}]\"', 19.99, 'pet', 'img3_2W1L7Y8S.png', 'https://www.CutiesPawNation.com/img/img2.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(9, '6X1S7H7H', 'Cat Castle', '\"[{\"text\":\"Plush covered condos provide maximum comfort for your furry friend to peacefully relax, lounge, or nap.\"},{\"text\":\"Sisal wrapped posts provide a healthy outlet for cats natural scratching instincts instead of using your furniture or carpet.\"},{\"text\":\"The castle\'s turret has hide-and-seek cutouts for those paw-swatting ambushes, and hanging plush toys for plenty of stimulating fun and entertainment.\"},{\"text\":\"Featuring a rustling\\/foil-crinkle blanket making it ideal for interactive play; encouraging exercise, stimulation and appeals to your cat\'s natural instinct to hunt prey.\"},{\"text\":\"A fluffy pom-pom dangling atop the cat tree gives your kitty the thrill of the hunt as she bats and swats it back and forth.\"}]\"', 124.53, 'pet', 'img9_6X1S7H7H.png', 'https://www.LifeStayWithPet.com/img/img12.png', 0, NULL, 0),
