(8, '7Q7G1O4E', 'Cat Climbing Tower', '\"[{\"text\":\"A small number of cats may not like to be close to or adapt to the product when they first come into contact with it. After half a month to a month of adaptation, they will like it. If the height of the product you buy is not suitable, you can contact us, we can put forward the appropriate solution according to your ceiling height.\"},{\"text\":\"This type is fit for celling height 107.5Inch-116.1Inch. Please confirm the roof height you want to set before purchasing.\"},{\"text\":\"The climbing tower with thick posts that reaches the ceiling stimulates the curiosity of cats, allowing your cat to climb trees as much as it likes, perfect for those who relieving lack of exercise and stress! If your cat gets tired, it can relax on the jump plate. It can also be used by multiple cats. The sturdy jump plate can withstand a weight of 15KG.\"},{\"text\":\"The posts of the cat tower are made of paper tubes. The whole body of the posts are wrapped in strong sisal rope. Cats can easily sharpen their claws. Cats won\\u2019t scratch pillars, walls, curtains. Sisal rope is durable, long-lasting, dust-free and clean.\"},{\"text\":\"The floor-to-ceiling cat tower that does not require drilling holes in the ceiling that is very easy to assemble! It is very space-saving that you can place it in a place such as a wall or a corner of a fence. The cat tower uses thick posts with a diameter of 9 cm, and the double-layer base board provides excellent stability.\"}]\"', 115.89, 'pet', 'img8_7Q7G1O4E.png', 'https://www.PetsParadiseStore.com/img/img9.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(6, '7I7S5D2F', 'Cat Condo', '\"[{\"text\":\"It\\u2019s a cat cove and cozy nap pad in one \\u2013 something every cat is sure to love!\"},{\"text\":\"Sturdy fabric walls set up in just moments, collapse down for easy storage.\"},{\"text\":\"Plush polyester pillows, 4 included, are simple to remove and machine washable.\"},{\"text\":\"Include fur beds.\"},{\"text\":\"Package Dimensions: 32.5 x 17 x 36 inches. Weight: 18.8 Pounds.\"}]\"', 69.99, 'pet', 'img6_7I7S5D2F.png', 'https://www.LovelyPetDistrict.com/img/img6.png', 0, NULL, 0),
