(9, '0E1M5H2J', 'Cat Litter Box', '\"[{\"text\":\"Sophistication In A Box: The Cat Litter Box is a sleek stunner that comes with a magnetic suction cover to keep kitty messes cleverly hidden. The cosy, hut-like design features a round entrance for cats to enter and exit through, and opens out effortlessly for easy cleaning.\"},{\"text\":\"The Ultimate Hidden Storage Compartment: Designed to blend in with the rest of your furniture without disrupting the overall tone of your home, the Cat Litter Box combines the cosy comforts of the litter box with an inner \\u2018cabinet\\u2019 and complimentary scoop for the ultimate all-in-one storage solution.\"},{\"text\":\"Simple Pull-Out Drawer For Easy Cleaning: The stylish cat litter box comes with one removable litter tray for hassle-free cleaning. With a non-stick surface that uses advanced plastic technology for effective odor-blocking, the lightweight tray provides all-day comfort to our kitties while ensuring easy clean-ups for their humans. Simply slide out, dump, and replace.\"},{\"text\":\"Curved Filter Aisle Reduces Tracking: Worried about litter being tracked across your floors? Well, consider yourself in good hands because the Cat Litter Box features innovative, grated steps on the interior to keep your kitty\'s dirty business confined within the box. Think of it as a built-in litter trapping mat and bid goodbye to frustrating litter tracks.\"},{\"text\":\"Compact and lightweight But With Big Space: Hidden storage compartment and complimentary scoop, Removable litter tray, Dimensions: 15 x 18 x 24 inch, Weight: 8.8 Ib Good for cats weight within 15 Ib.\"}]\"', 132, 'pet', 'img9_0E1M5H2J.png', 'https://www.PetLoveMaster.com/img/img10.png', 0, NULL, 0),
