(2, '7J7J2G1R', 'Cat Toys', '\"[{\"text\":\"Excites & Entices Cats: Give your feline friend the thrill of the chase with this value pack of 10 Critters. The mischief of these soft plush mice toys is sure to provide your cat with hours of swatting, batting and chasing fun!\"},{\"text\":\"Filled With Pure Catnip: The easy-to-carry plush design entices your kitty to play while the flappy ears and ribbon tails keep them engaged. Plus, they\'re lightweight so you can toss them easily and watch your little hunter go, and are stuffed with 100% pure, potent, chemical-free and pesticide-free catnip for a boost of purrfect excitement to keep your pal coming back for more.\"},{\"text\":\"Combines Playtime With Exercise: Make interactive playtime irresistible and bring these cat toys out anytime your kitty needs a boost of healthy exercise to support toned muscles, or let your pal play independently since they\'re easy to catch, carry and bat.\"}]\"', 5.95, 'pet', 'img2_7J7J2G1R.png', 'https://www.AllTheBestForPets.com/img/img1.png', 0, NULL, 0),
