(5, '4L3Y1J1H', 'Ceramic Dog Bowl', '\"[{\"text\":\"Pet dishes don\\u2019t have to be an eyesore; why not treat yourself and your pet to a quirky, sweet food and water bowl? Complete with sweet sayings and a charming, imperfect font, each of these pet dishes is fit for a king. Big enough to hold food and water for the day but small enough to not become an eyesore in your home, this is a pet dish you\'ll love seeing every day. Not only are they precious, but they are also very functional. Stoneware is an ideal material, as it is more durable than typical porcelain ceramic wares and can hold up over time like plastic, but without the dangerous chemicals. The heavy weight prevents slipping and spillage, so food and water stay in the bowl and not on your floor. When it\'s time to clean your dishes, just toss these pet bowls in the washer for fuss-free cleaning and sanitizing.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 8 x 8 x 3.5 inches; Weight: 3.46 Pounds; Material: Stoneware; Color: White; Target Species: Cat, Dog\"}]\"', 49.95, 'pet', 'img5_4L3Y1J1H.png', 'https://www.CharmingPetStore.com/img/img5.png', 0, NULL, 0),
