(2, '6G5W3Y1U', 'Chew Ring for Dog', '\"[{\"text\":\"Textured Ring Shape \\u2013 Unique shape with enticing textures is easy to hold and satisfies dogs natural urge to chew.\"},{\"text\":\"Made Of Durable Nylon \\u2013 Long lasting dog chew toy challenges even the most aggressive chewers and discourages destructive chewing.\"},{\"text\":\"Promotes Dog Dental Health \\u2013 Ridges and nubs help prevent plaque and tartar buildup as dogs chew.\"},{\"text\":\"For Extra-Large Dogs \\u2013 Chew toy created for dogs 50+ pounds. Irresistible Flavor Medley \\u2013 Flavored dog chew toy combines all of your dog\'s favorite tastes in one.\"},{\"text\":\"Chew Toy Dimensions: Out of package measures 6.5\\\" long x 2 \\\" wide x 2.06\\\" high.\"}]\"', 5.95, 'pet', 'img2_6G5W3Y1U.png', 'https://www.ThePetHappniess.com/img/img1.png', 0, NULL, 0),
