(3, '2N1C3S2Q', 'Cleaner Fish Tank Kit', '\"[{\"text\":\"Hand-Held Design: Lightweight & convenient, well-formed shape & compact structure,with 2 inlet pipes (15.74 inch*2) , it\'s suitable for installing and operating fish tanks of different sizes. Tips: Fish tank cleaner is better for aquariums depth below 31.5 inches.\"},{\"text\":\"Prevent Blocking: Aquarium gravel cleaner can change water to keep water cleaner, with a filter basket in the tube, avoid blocking by gravel. Not only effectively separate and remove debris, but also protect your lovely fish or small gravel from suck out of the aquarium.\"},{\"text\":\"Easy To Use: Press the air button switch of the aquarium siphon cleaner to pump water , ensure that the inlet pipe is partially filled with water, then observe the outlet hose until the water automatically flows out quickly, last hold the aquarium gravel cleaner to clean up the place you want to.\"},{\"text\":\"Variety Of Accessories: Soft hose, water flow clamp, glass scraper , hose clamp and anti-backflow valve design. Tips: Valve is already installed, not need to install it again.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 16.15 x 4.41 x 2.52 inches; Weight: 13.93 Ounces.\"}]\"', 19.99, 'pet', 'img3_2N1C3S2Q.png', 'https://www.LittlePetGathering.com/img/img2.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(10, '3K2O4B6C', 'Clipper for Horses', '\"[{\"text\":\"Powerful enough to complete full body clips on horses, slick shearing sheep, fitting cattle, and general show clipping on all livestock animals.\"},{\"text\":\"Ventilated, self-cleaning head prevents blades from overheating while the user-friendly tensioning system makes it easier than ever to set correct blade tension.\"},{\"text\":\"Cleaning and maintenance are easy with the removable and replaceable air filter while a 16 foot cord allows for flexibility and movement throughout clipping.\"},{\"text\":\"Comes equipped with blade, which has a clipping surface width of 3 inches for quick clipping and a cut length of 1.4 mm (3\\/64 inches)\"},{\"text\":\"This package also includes a 2.1-ounce bottle of oil, clipper cleaning brush, and a spare filter.\"}]\"', 141, 'pet', 'img10_3K2O4B6C.png', 'https://www.DreamPetWorld.com/img/img12.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(2, '2Y6A1A6A', 'Collapsible Dog Bowl, 2 Pack', '\"[{\"text\":\"COLLAPSIBLE DESIGN: Convenient collapsible design for saving space, simply stretch and fold away,which are good for traveling,hiking,camping.\"},{\"text\":\"PORTABLE & CONVENIENT: The collapsible dog bowls are great pet travel bowls, lightweight and easy to carry with climbing buckle. It can attach to belt loop, backpack, leash or other locations.Suitable for outdoor acitivies.They also can be used as indoor dog \\/ cat food bowl.\"},{\"text\":\"DURABLE & SAFE : These dog bowls are made of high quality silicone , odorless, durable and friendly.\"},{\"text\":\"SIZE: 5.1 X 3.5 X 2.1 inch ( 5.1*3.5*2.1 inch), small sized bowl holds up to 12 fluid ounces of water or 1.5 cups of pet food. Please note: Small collapsible dog bowls suitable for small puppies, dogs.Large sized bowls for medium to large dogs.\"},{\"text\":\"EASY TO CLEAN: Dishwasher safe, in order to reduce unnecessary waste, these compact puppy food bowls can be rinsed or wiped clean after each use, and have a great longevity.\"}]\"', 6.95, 'pet', 'img2_2Y6A1A6A.png', 'https://www.PetTreatmentMaster.com/img/img21.png', 0, NULL, 0),
