(2, '2O8C6U8E', 'GPS Dog Collar Holder(2 Pack)', '\"[{\"text\":\"    \\u3010COMPATIBLE\\u3011The Airtag Holder Case is professionally designed for Apple Air tags 2021, so your could hanging it to the 0.8-1.2 inch pets collar\\/pet loop holders easily, which keeps the Air tag stays with the pet strap, to avoids the drop and unnecessary drag.\"},{\"text\":\"    \\u3010COMFORTABLE FOR PETS\\u3011Your Pets will feel uncomfortable if something is hanging and shaking under the pet\'s collar. BUT this one will solve all of its concerns and make your pets feel more at ease when running and won\'t leave any room for your dog to chew\"},{\"text\":\"    \\u3010PREMIUM MATERIAL\\u3011This airtag dog holder is made of eco-friendly flexible and soft liquid silicone, it is very easy to clean, washable, anti-fingerprint, Scratch-resistant, and Drop protection performance.\"},{\"text\":\"    \\u3010EASY TO USE\\u3011This dog airtag holder skin cover features an independent design to be easy to use under the Cat \\/ Dog Collars and pet loop holder, also it could keep your air tags stay closed and avoid the Airtag case sliding out accidentally. You can attach it to your backpack\\/bag, elder\'s belt, child\'s schoolbag, dog\\/cat collars, or pet loop holder, and more. Easily keep tracking of anything you want.\"},{\"text\":\"    \\u3010USE OCCASION\\u3011The ID Tags & Airtag Collar Accessories is a two-way opening design so that you can attach it to your dog\\/cat collars or pet loop holder, Collars, Harnesses & Leashes, and more. Easily keep tracking of anything you want.\"}]\"', 6.25, 'pet', 'img2_2O8C6U8E.png', 'https://www.FlurryFunKingdom.com/img/img20.png', 0, NULL, 0),
