(5, '2K7J4T4Q', 'Grooming Tools for Small & Large Pets', '\"[{\"text\":\"Our grooming clipper is a new type of 33 teeth titanium-ceramic blade combining with the ceramic movable blade , including a curly wavy coat and long coat design, so the ceramic clipper can easy cut the double heavy coat. Compared with the traditional 24-tooth cutter head, the cutting is smoother, the heat dissipation is more uniform and the durability is more durable.\"},{\"text\":\"Usually a part of pets get stressed and uneasy by the sound and the vibration of the pet clippers. But our pet grooming tools are only about 50 db when they work, to help the pet feel at ease, not afraid cut hair any more. You don\'t need to worry about scaring and hurting them.\"},{\"text\":\"Heavy-duty gear for proper powerful cut, with stable and steady control. This dog hair clipper provides substantial power and speed without producing additional heat or noise. Three-speed rotary motor for performance that pros demand. 2200mAh High Capacity Li-ion Battery, charging for 3 hours and can sustain use of 3-4 hours to accommodate a full-body clipping on small and medium dogs or cats.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 9.96 x 6.81 x 2.32 inches; Weight: 8.11 ounces; Color: Black;\"}]\"', 49.95, 'pet', 'img5_2K7J4T4Q.png', 'https://www.LoveOnlyPetStore.com/img/img5.jpg', 0, NULL, 0),
(4, '0X6Z8Q4E', 'Guinea Pig & Hamster House', '\"[{\"text\":\"3 Pack Hamster Accessories:1 hamster bridge,1 Wooden Ladder,1 hamster house(5.5\\\"L x 5.5\\\"W x 8.7\\\"H.).\"},{\"text\":\"Hideout: Fun nesting and resting, provide a safe habitat for your small animal with lookout holes .With ladder and climbing wall Gym,Sleeping nest, balcony,allows your beloved guinea pig to do more exercise.\"},{\"text\":\"Wooden Ladder: Made From Selected Hardwood sticks, strung and formed by 2 of flexible metal wires,it\'s bendable and takes shapes, like a climbing ladder, bedding or sand area divider, suspension bridge toys.\"},{\"text\":\"Hamster House: Recommended for hamster, guinea pig,chinchillas,mice, gerbil, rat.... It\'s adjusted to different shapes to organize pet\'s playground.\"}]\"', 24.99, 'pet', 'img4_0X6Z8Q4E.png', 'https://www.ThePetHappniess.com/img/img3.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(5, '7H2W3S2U', 'Guinea Pig Cage Liners', '\"[{\"text\":\"This guinea pig liner is made of four layers: soft & comfortable short fleece top layer which is perfect for the piggies\' little feet, highly absorbent fabric middle layer that helps to keeps the surface dry, breathable & waterproof TPU layer, and anti-slip bottom layer.\"},{\"text\":\"Package Dimensions: 10.5 x 10.5 x 6 inches; Weight: 2.19 Pounds; Color: Dark and Light Gray\"}]\"', 49.95, 'pet', 'img5_7H2W3S2U.png', 'https://www.PetTreatmentMaster.com/img/img5.png', 0, NULL, 0),
