(10, '1S7N8R5L', 'Hoof Nipper', '\"[{\"text\":\"Our hoof clamps are designed to provide you with high-quality, professional tools, so that you can easily cut through any hoof, thus making it easier to care for the feet of ungulates.\"},{\"text\":\"The hoof repair tool kit is made of strong, durable, high-quality metal material that can be used for a long time and is not easy to break.\"},{\"text\":\"By increasing the length according to the principle of leverage, the sturdy hoof pliers can easily cut into the hardest and thickest hoof.\"},{\"text\":\"The handle of the hoof trimmer is ergonomic, labor-saving, comfortable, and easy to hold and use. Increase the user-friendliness when clamping the hoof.\"},{\"text\":\"Our high-performance hoof clamps are very suitable for hoof care of horses, sheep and goats, pigs, cows, llamas, alpacas, etc!\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 15 x 3.4 x 0.4 inches. Weight: 1.65 Pounds.\"}]\"', 149, 'pet', 'img10_1S7N8R5L.png', 'https://www.VIPFunPetShop.com/img/img13.png', 0, NULL, 0),
