(5, '1G1K0E5B', 'Horse Grooming Kit', '\"[{\"text\":\"7-piece assortment of grooming essentials in a durable nylon tote bag.\"},{\"text\":\"Tote features six exterior pockets for added storage.\"},{\"text\":\"Features a convenient top Drawstring closure and plastic feet that protect bottom of bag.\"},{\"text\":\"Comfortable webbing handles, and an adjustable, padded shoulder strap.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 11.81 x 11.73 x 7.01 inches. Weight: 1.24 Kilograms.\"}]\"', 49.95, 'pet', 'img5_1G1K0E5B.png', 'https://www.VIPFunPetShop.com/img/img5.png', 0, NULL, 0),
