(8, '0G6G2H3E', 'Horse Winter Blanket', '\"[{\"text\":\"60 inches. Rainbow.\"},{\"text\":\"Heavy-weight winter blanket is constructed with a rip-stop waterproof, windproof, and breathable poly outer shell with 210 lining.\"},{\"text\":\"400 grams of poly fill keeps your horse warm and dry in the winter. Blanket features adjustable double buckle front with snap closure, cross surcingles, neck adjust, and elastic leg straps for a secure and snug fit.\"},{\"text\":\"Tail flap for added protection. Shoulder gussets offers freedom of movement. Fleece wither protection. Nickle plated hardware.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 12 x 11.25 x 7.5 inches; Weight: 7.5 Pounds.\"}]\"', 109, 'pet', 'img8_0G6G2H3E.png', 'https://www.PetsEnjoyment.com/img/img8.png', 0, NULL, 0),
