(8, '1S1H7F4L', 'Pet Carrier', '\"[{\"text\":\"Airline Approved Cat Carrier: Travel carrier is airline approved and perfect for travel by plane, subway, or car. The cat carrier measures 19.3 inches long x 12.6 inches wide x 11.8 inches high, recommended for pets up to 8 kg.\"},{\"text\":\"24L Underwater Carrier: Underwater shape design with clear door allows pets to enjoy the scenery on the go. The arched inner wall allows cats to roll freely inside. Integrated 0.27L food container and soft padding allow pets to enjoy a comfortable ride.\"},{\"text\":\"Breathable and Comfortable: Symmetrical air vents on both sides + large area vents behind provide optimal airflow. The 3V electric fan is built into the top of the baby carrier, the 4300 speed fan brings more fresh air to the cat carrier, let the pets have a comfortable travel.\"},{\"text\":\"Pet Night Light: Built-in soft LED night lights, you just need to touch the light control button to gradually illuminate the internal space, allowing your pet to clearly see the surroundings and allowing you to see your pet at night . Powered by battery.\"},{\"text\":\"Hard Sided Pet Carrier: Made of ABS and PC, durable and waterproof, compared to the carrier made of cloth, it is easy to clean. Comes with TPE material handle, comfortable and portable. Ideal for small breed dogs and cats of average size.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 19.75 x 14 x 12.5 inches; Weight: 5.9 Pounds.\"}]\"', 106.58, 'pet', 'img8_1S1H7F4L.png', 'https://www.PetsEnjoyment.com/img/img7.png', 0, NULL, 0),
