(7, '4U1L3C3O', 'Pigeon Cage', '\"[{\"text\":\"The pigeon pairing cage is used for pairing of homing pigeons. There is a partition in the middle, which allows the pigeons you want to pair to quickly adapt and get estrus. When the male pigeons keep calling and the female pigeons keep flapping their wings, the partition can be pulled out to make the pigeons pair successfully.\"},{\"text\":\"Pigeon cage Multi-purpose, when the estrus period is over, you can add a partition in the middle to become two independent cages for pigeons to rest, or to hatch and raise young pigeons, without affecting each other. When the estrus is coming, you can remove the partitions and become a love nest for pigeons.\"},{\"text\":\"Pigeon cage has 2 sliding doors. When you need it, you can put the door down. When you don\'t need it, you can slide it up and hide it. The bottom has a detachable tray that can be pulled out for cleaning, which effectively protects the pigeon cage. Of hygiene. With a pull-out partition in the middle, it is suitable for pigeon breeding in all periods.\"},{\"text\":\"The cage is made of High-strength plastic .Can be rinsed with water It has a long service life, is safe, environmentally friendly, non-toxic, and is made of natural materials, which is good for pigeons\\u2019 health. It is also very durable and can be stacked with multiple cages to fill the entire wall, which saves space, and is conducive to the group living of pigeons and cultivates the feelings between pigeons. Convenient management and breeding.\"}]\"', 89.95, 'pet', 'img7_4U1L3C3O.png', 'https://www.YourPetTime.com/img/img7.png', 0, NULL, 0),
