(2, '4B1B0W5Q', 'Portable Outdoor Dog Shower', '\"[{\"text\":\"100% FOOD GRADE SILICONE \\u2764\\ufe0f Dog use silicone shower head is made of dishwasher-safe food grade silicone, PVC and BPA free\"},{\"text\":\"OUTDOOR\\/INDOOR PORTABLE SHOWER \\u2764\\ufe0f Turn plastic soda bottle into a convenient outdoor hiking gear; Fill your bottle with water, and gently place the bottle shower head on the plastic bottleneck, tilt and squeeze it. Easily clean the dirt, sand, and mud on your body for your dirty dog, children, and even yourself\"},{\"text\":\"SUITABLE FOR PLASTIC BOTTLES \\u2764\\ufe0f Suitable for any standard PET soda bottle from 16 ounces to 2 liters; The diameter of the lid hole is suitable for most plastic bottles. Use a 2-liter bottle, and the shower time is more than one minute\"},{\"text\":\"MULTIFUNCTIONAL TRAVEL SHOWER \\u2764\\ufe0f If you like to go out for outings, this travel shower is a must-have choice. Just fill it with water and squeeze it, and you can use small amounts of water to clean and \\\"cool down\\\" whenever and wherever possible\"},{\"text\":\"PLANT WATERING TOOL \\u2764\\ufe0f Water bottle cap sprinkler can also be used as a garden plant watering tool. You can use it to water your plants, it will provide an easy to control water flow, suitable for just sprouting seedlings and mature plants \"}]\"', 6.95, 'pet', 'img2_4B1B0W5Q.png', 'https://www.FluffyPetStorePro.com/img/img21.png', 0, NULL, 0),
