(2, '6K6R0N6N', 'Treat Bag', '\"[{\"text\":\"Treat-training tool: clip-on dog treat pouch allows pet parents to quickly reward good behavior on the spot by attaching to belt or pocket.\"},{\"text\":\"Easy-open pouch: drawstring closure is easy to open with one hand for quick access to dog treats.\"},{\"text\":\"Treat storage: holds 1 cup of dogs\' favorite treats and seals via drawstring closure to ensure freshness.\"},{\"text\":\"Heavy-duty material: durable pack-cloth dog treat bag is water-resistant to keep treats dry and reinforced with a rip-stop liner for lasting quality.\"},{\"text\":\"Holds more than treats: clip-on dog training pouch is ideal for stowing small toys or waste bags in addition to small training treats.\"},{\"text\":\"Distraction-free training: clip-on treat tote is small and discreet to keep dogs focused on playtime or training.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 1 x 5 x 8 inches. Weight: 0.8 Ounces.\"}]\"', 6.25, 'pet', 'img2_6K6R0N6N.png', 'https://www.LovelyPetIsland.com/img/img15.png', 0, NULL, 0),
