(10, '3P0K3V7U', 'Coding Robot for Kids', '\"[{\"text\":\"Dash teaches code in kid speak for girls and boys ages 6-11. A child\\u2019s first real robot friend. The physical robot comes with access to a virtual Dash robot that kids can program in a rich 3-D environment on screen.\"},{\"text\":\"Includes: 1 Dash robot, 2 connectors, 1 USB charging cable. Dash and dot do not contain a camera. This Dash unit contains more working memory than before and an 18% longer battery life.\"},{\"text\":\"We provide a suite of tools that turbocharge how kids interact with Dash and the Blockly App that powers him.\"},{\"text\":\"In addition to progress tracking for the series of coding puzzles inside Blockly, it includes 60 story-based, standards-aligned Math activities as well as a virtual Dash robot that kids can program in a rich 3-D environment on screen.\"},{\"text\":\"Free apps for Apple iOS, Android OS, and Fire OS: program Dash to move, dance, make sounds, avoid obstacles, and more.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 6.69 x 7.16 x 6.33; Weight: 2.65 pounds; Age range: 72-120 months; Color: Blue and Orange\"}]\"', 149, 'toy', 'img10_3P0K3V7U.png', 'https://www.FunPlayToyz.com/img/img13.png', 0, NULL, 0),
