(8, '2C4X2I8R', 'Kid Picnic Play Table', '\"[{\"text\":\"Sized right for younger children, this indoor\\/outdoor table \\u201cunlocks\\u201d and folds for portability or storage; This picnic table set is a perfect present for your kid\'s birthday, Christmas.\"},{\"text\":\"Stay and Play longer outside by adding an umbrella (not included); Give your child a space of their own in your backyard to eat, play, and relax with this picnic table set.\"},{\"text\":\"No tools are required to set it up or take it down; Snaps together easily without tools, folds flat when disassembled to store in a garage, closet, or shed.\"},{\"text\":\"Your kids can share their happy time with friends together No worry about a sudden shower; The umbrella is also removable to enjoy the sunshine.;The recommended age is 18 months to 5 years.\"},{\"text\":\"Kids can use this table as a picnic table, craft table, snack table, or game table; it sets up and folds down in a snap for storing; Wipe with a damp cloth to clean.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 27.2 x 27 x 18.25 inches. Weight: 9.04 pounds.\"}]\"', 109, 'toy', 'img8_2C4X2I8R.png', 'https://www.FunfulToyNation.com/img/img8.png', 0, NULL, 0),
