(8, '2Y2A2Y3T', 'Kids Balance Bike', '\"[{\"text\":\"Beginner Bikes: The petal free bikes cultivate confidence and encourage intuitive riding while developing balance and coordination. With this in mind, kids familiar with a balance bike will more easily transition to a \\\"big-kid\\\" set of wheels.\"},{\"text\":\"Safe & Lightweight: This safe beginner\'s bike reduces the risk of injury by keeping feet and frame low to the ground. Pint-size cyclists are able to zip around while practicing their balancing skills on their legs instead of relying on training wheels.\"},{\"text\":\"Durable Frame: A low stand-over height, step-through frame. The high-tensile strength steel frame and fork are virtually indestructible, but your child is not, so always strap on a helmet!\"},{\"text\":\"Adjustable Seat: The handles and seat post are adjustable, accounting for all inevitable growth spurts! Fits children from 2 to 3 years old with adjustable seat posts and handlebars.\"}]\"', 119, 'toy', 'img8_2Y2A2Y3T.png', 'https://www.JoyfulToyMaster.com/img/img10.png', 0, NULL, 0),
