(10, '6L3A7K3F', 'Kitchen Set for Kids', '\"[{\"text\":\"Fun And Education: Designs include ovens, sinks, Notepad\\uff0cwashers and water dispensers, lockers and fun stoves to inspire creativity and imagination.Suitable for children ages 3+.\"},{\"text\":\"Easy To Assemble:The assembly instructions for the children\'s kitchen are easy to read, and each board has a number that matches the instructions, making it easy for children and parents to experience the fun of assembly.\"},{\"text\":\"Safety Material: The toy kitchen set uses mdf board, so your little one can enjoy harmless fun in the next few years.\"},{\"text\":\"Oversized Kitchen:Parents can accompany their children to play together,Can accompany children to grow up happily.Cultivate their hands-on, creative and collaborative skills in entertainment.And, leave them a good childhood memory.\"}]\"', 141, 'toy', 'img10_6L3A7K3F.png', 'https://www.LivesWithToy.com/img/img12.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(5, '2O4Q3K2O', 'LCD Writing Tablet', '\"[{\"text\":\"Eye Protection Color Screen: The LCD writing tablet adopts 2019 LCD pressure-sensitive technology and has 10-inch LCD colorful screen, easy for viewing and graffiti, free child\\u2019s imagination. This drawing tablet without radiation, no glare, safe and comfortable, even kids use for a long time. Educational birthday girl gifts.\"},{\"text\":\"Environmental Friendly: The doodle board can be writing 100,000 times, avoid waste of paper and pencils, avoid the extra expense, no more mess at home, it\\u2019s good choice for kids toy. The writing board drawing tablet comes with built-in battery, has 6 months life span, can be replaced when exhausted, without charging or plugging in power.\"},{\"text\":\"Easy To Use: The writing tablet creates lines as writing and drawing on paper, the different thickness based on how hard you push with stylus, nails, or any hard thing. Emptying the screen content in one second by press earse button, acheive time-saving and convenient using. Click lock key of doodle board to save the content.\"},{\"text\":\"Portable And Durable: The drawing board for kids is made of durable plastic, plus round corner design, anti-fall and anti-shock, no need to worry kids drop it. The drawing tablet weights only 150 grams, easy to carry, place in school bags, handbags, travel bags. The doodle board also can be used in multiple places: airplane, car, restaurant, sofa, etc. The perfect travel toy for toddlers.\"},{\"text\":\"Educational And Learning Toy For Kids:  The battery door on the back of the drawing board is fixed by a screw, which is safer for children.LCD writing tablet can be used as a doodle board, drawing tablet, writing board, doodle pad, kid\\u2019s drawing pad, toddler drawing board,graphic aids, graphic tablet, magic children\'s board, educational toys, toddler girl toys, baby girl gifts. Perfect Choice for kids as gift for back to school, birthday, Thanksgiving Day, Easter and any occa