(9, '5A4S7W0C', 'Toy Kitchen', '\"[{\"text\":\"Includes: Wet and dry activity areas, hob and \\u201cmud kitchen\\u201d stencils, oven door, removable splash tub, storage, hanging rail, chalkboard, serving station, and stainless steel pots, pans, and whisk.\"},{\"text\":\"Backyard Chef: Mix some mud in the plastic sink, cook on the stencil-your-own oven burners, bake using the oven with a door that opens and closes, hang up utensils on the rail, and make something fun!\"},{\"text\":\"Fun For Children: Boys and girls will love cooking with this wooden playset! Whether it\\u2019ll be a BBQ or a bakery, the accessories with this set will let the little ones make the best pretend food.\"},{\"text\":\"Cute Kitchen: There\\u2019s room for 2 to 3 kids ages 3 years old and up. Made from FSC certified pressure treated European timber wood. 44\\\" x 38\\\" x 43\\\". Bowl can hold 10 kg of mud or 7 liters of water.\"}]\"', 129.87, 'toy', 'img9_5A4S7W0C.png', 'https://www.JoyfulToyMaster.com/img/img13.png', 0, NULL, 0),
