(7, '4C6M1M5V', 'Wooden Farm Playset', '\"[{\"text\":\"Encourages Social & Emotional Roleplay - Designed to build confidence, creativity and social skills through fun, imaginative role play, encourage kids to get into a character and act out real life scenarios, learning through their play.\"},{\"text\":\"Great Learning Toy Gift For Kids Ages 3 And Older - This playset is an exceptional gift for any kid 3 years of age and older. Add berties tractor & farmer budkins to round out the hands-on play experience and give kids another engaging option for screen-free fun.\"},{\"text\":\"Designed For Interactive & Imaginative Play - Kids love playing together with this fun, colourful scenario and role play toy. The durably designed wooden farm playset develops and encourages your child to learn turn taking skills as well as social interaction.\"},{\"text\":\"High Quality, Eco-Friendly Safe Toy - Wooden toy beautifully decorated with colourful non-toxic paints and tested to the highest safety standards. Made from durable, sustainable rubberwood, allowing long-lasting fun, whilst caring for our planet.\"},{\"text\":\"Product Details & Description - Measures 22. 83\\\" X 20. 47\\\" X 9. 44\\\". This playset is recommended for kids ages 3 years and older.\"}]\"', 89.99, 'toy', 'img7_4C6M1M5V.png', 'https://www.LovelyToyPro.com/img/img6.png', 0, NULL, 0),
