(3, '3B0U5C8L', 'Wooden Lacing Beads', '\"[{\"text\":\"Lacing Beads set is composed of 30 brightly colored wooden beads in a variety of shapes, 2 colorful laces, and a wooden storage case.\"},{\"text\":\"Our wooden bead play set includes beads in five distinct shapes that are easy for little hands to grasp. The laces are thin enough to allow the beads to fit seamlessly.\"},{\"text\":\"Kids beading set helps children develop strong fine motor, cognitive, and visual perception skills, while promoting hand-eye coordination. These beads set makes an exceptional gift for kids from 3 to 5 years.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 9.2 x 7.7 x 1.7 inches. Weight: 15.5 ounces.\"}]\"', 19.99, 'toy', 'img3_3B0U5C8L.png', 'https://www.PlayExcellenceToy.com/img/img2.png', 0, NULL, 0),
