(4, '6I6H4P5F', 'Wooden Musical Toy', '\"[{\"text\":\"Unleash your baby\'s creativity with their first piano toy; wooden piano magically makes music with just a touch; includes 3 sheets of music and 6 different songs.\"},{\"text\":\"Practice color coordination by matching the color-coded notes on the sheets to the keys on the piano; with 2 modes of play, babies can create their own original songs or discover familiar ones.\"},{\"text\":\"Volume control allows you to set the music to \\u201clow\\u201d or \\u201chigh\\u201d depending on your environment and preference; higher end quality speakers ensure clear sound at either volume.\"},{\"text\":\"Ideal for ages 6-36 months; great gift idea for first birthday, toddler Christmas gift, or \\\"just because\\\" gifting; the fun lasts through toddler years.\"},{\"text\":\"Made from child safe and durable materials; assembled dimensions 12x5x9\\\"; wipe clean with damp cloth and mild soap; do not immerse in water; powered by 3 AA batteries (not included).\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 12 x 5 x 9 inches. Weight: 2.75 pounds.\"}]\"', 24.99, 'toy', 'img4_6I6H4P5F.png', 'https://www.ToyHyper.com/img/img3.png', 0, NULL, 0);
