(10, '8X1K6E7B', 'Wooden Walker Toy', '\"[{\"text\":\"80% Rubberwood, 16% Plywood, 3% Rubber, 1% Stainless Steel.\"},{\"text\":\"COLORFUL UNIQUE DESIGN: A great toy for a toddler finding their feet. A unique baby walker in a soft cloud shape with 45 rubber wood blocks painted in delightful water stained rainbow colors. The Rainbow Cloud Walker encourages new walkers to stay on their feet. The sturdy wooden construction offers support to develop their confidence, help with balance and stability as little ones learn to walk.\"},{\"text\":\"CREATIVE WOODEN EDUCATIONAL TOYS FOR TODDLERS: Range of wooden toddler toys encourage early learning through play, developing hand eye coordination and confidence. Suitable for one year olds and older. Makes for the perfect educational wooden toy! The traditional wooden rainbow blocks are a classic and fun way to stimulate psychological and fine motor skills. This baby walker encourages shape recognition, develops hand-eye coordination and imagination.\"},{\"text\":\"HIGH QUALITY, ECO-FRIENDLY AND SAFE EDUCATIONAL TOYS: Decorated with non-toxic paints and tested to the highest safety standards. We use sustainable materials, non-toxic paints and ensure kid safe edges for safe play every day. Sensory layers of colors, sounds, textures and discovery foster curiosity and encourage early learning through play. Our toys quickly become well loved family favourites, for generations to come. Suitable for 12+ months.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 15.55 x 13.5 x 6.69 inches. Weight: 9.06 pounds.\"}]\"', 149, 'toy', 'img10_8X1K6E7B.png', 'https://www.PlayExcellenceToy.com/img/img13.png', 0, NULL, 0),
(9, '6T2I4L0X', 'Wooden Work Bench', '\"[{\"text\":\"A saw, a hammer, a screw driver, a spanner, a spirit level, 2 bolts, 2 screws, 2 nails and a piece of wood. The worktop has a flatbed circular saw, a measuring gauge and a vice. Back wall features a shelf to tidy tools, hook for the saw & detailed illustrations.\"},{\"text\":\"Kids love playing together with this fun, colorful scenario and role play wooden toy car set! Encourages your child to learn turn taking skills as well as social and language development.\"},{\"text\":\"Decorated with non-toxic paints and tested to the highest safety standards. Using natural materials, including replenishable legal quality smooth rubber-wood and an array of techniques from hand screen printing to water staining, these detailed hand-finished toys are unique and loved by little hand.\"},{\"text\":\"Dimensions: 16.57 x 27.64 x 3.58 inches. Weight: 19.58 pounds.\"}]\"', 139, 'toy', 'img9_6T2I4L0X.png', 'https://www.FavoriteFunToys.com/img/img11.png', 0, NULL, 0),
